#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Actions"
msgstr "操作"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:2
msgid "You can manage actions on your clients in a number of different ways."
msgstr "您可以通过多种不同的方式管理对客户端执行的操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:3
msgid ""
"For Salt clients, you can schedule automated recurring actions to apply the "
"highstate or an arbitrary set of custom states to clients on a specified "
"schedule.  You can apply recurring actions to individual clients, to all "
"clients in a system group, or to an entire organization."
msgstr ""
"对于 Salt 客户端，您可以安排自动重复性操作，以按照指定的日程安排将 Highstate "
"或任意一组自定义状态应用于客户端。您可以将重复性操作应用于单个客户端、系统组"
"中的所有客户端或整个组织。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:4
msgid ""
"On both Salt and traditional clients, you can set actions to be performed in "
"a particular order by creating action chains.  Action chains can be created "
"and edited ahead of time, and scheduled to run at a time that suits you."
msgstr ""
"在 Salt 和传统客户端上，都可以通过创建操作链来设置要按特定顺序执行的操作。可"
"以提前创建和编辑操作链，并将其安排为在适当的时间运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:5
msgid ""
"You can also perform remote commands on one or more of your Salt clients.  "
"Remote commands allows you to issue commands to individual Salt clients, or "
"to all clients that match a search term."
msgstr ""
"您还可以在一个或多个 Salt 客户端上执行远程命令。使用远程命令可以向单个 Salt "
"客户端或者与搜索词匹配的所有客户端发出命令。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recurring Actions"
msgstr "重复性操作"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:7
msgid ""
"You can apply recurring actions on individual Salt clients, to a system "
"group, or to all clients in an organization."
msgstr "可以对单个 Salt 客户端、系统组、组织中的所有客户端应用重复性操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Currently, {productname} supports the following action types as recurring "
"actions:"
msgstr "{productname} 目前支持将以下操作类型作为重复性操作："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:9
msgid "[parameter]``Highstate:`` Execute the highstate."
msgstr "[parameter]``Highstate``：执行 Highstate。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:10
msgid ""
"[parameter]``Custom state:`` Execute a set of custom states. A custom state "
"can be either an internal state provided by {productname}, or a "
"configuration channel created by a user."
msgstr ""
"[parameter]``自定义状态``：执行一组自定义状态。自定义状态可以是 "
"{productname} 提供的内部状态，也可以是用户创建的配置通道。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:11
msgid ""
"For more information about configuration channels, see xref:client-"
"configuration:configuration-management.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关配置通道的详细信息，请参见 xref:client-configuration:configuration-"
"management.adoc[]。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a New Recurring Action"
msgstr "过程：创建新的重复性操作"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:13
msgid ""
"To apply a recurring action to an individual client, navigate to "
"[guimenu]``Systems``, click the client to configure schedules for, and "
"navigate to the menu:[Recurring Actions] tab."
msgstr ""
"要将重复性操作应用于单个客户端，请导航到[guimenu]``系统``，单击要为其配置日程"
"安排的客户端，然后导航到menu:[重复性操作]选项卡。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:14
msgid ""
"To apply a recurring action to a system group, navigate to menu:"
"Systems[System Groups], select the group to configure schedules for, and "
"navigate to menu:[Recurring Actions] tab."
msgstr ""
"要将重复性操作应用于系统组，请导航到menu:系统[系统组]，选择要为其配置日程安排"
"的组，然后导航到menu:[重复性操作]选项卡。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:15
msgid "Click btn:[Create]."
msgstr "单击 btn:[创建]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:16
msgid "Select an action type from the [guimenu]``Action Type`` dropdown."
msgstr "从[guimenu]``操作类型``下拉列表中选择操作类型。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:17
msgid "Type a name for the new schedule."
msgstr "键入新日程安排的名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:18
msgid "Choose the frequency of the recurring action:"
msgstr "选择重复性操作的频率："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:19
msgid "[guimenu]``Hourly:`` Type the minute of each hour."
msgstr "[guimenu]``每小时：``键入每小时内过去的分钟数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:20
msgid ""
"For example, [parameter]``15`` runs the action at fifteen minutes past every "
"hour."
msgstr "例如，如果指定 [parameter]``15``，则在每小时过去 15 分钟后运行操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:21
msgid "[guimenu]``Daily:`` Select the time of each day."
msgstr "[guimenu]``每日：``选择每日的时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:22
msgid ""
"For example, [parameter]``01:00`` runs the action at 0100 every day, in the "
"timezone of the {productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"例如，如果指定 [parameter]``01:00``，则在 {productname} Server 所在时区的每"
"日 01:00 运行操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:23
msgid ""
"[guimenu]``Weekly:`` Select the day of the week and the time of the day, to "
"execute the action every week at the specified time."
msgstr ""
"[guimenu]``每周：``选择星期日期和该日期中的时间，以便在每周的指定时间执行操"
"作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:24
msgid ""
"[guimenu]``Monthly:`` Select the day of the month and the time of the day, "
"to execute the action every month at the specified time."
msgstr ""
"[guimenu]``每月：``选择月份日期和该日期中的时间，以便在每月的指定时间执行操"
"作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:25
msgid ""
"[guimenu]``Custom Quartz format:`` For more detailed options, enter a custom "
"quartz string."
msgstr ""
"[guimenu]``自定义 Quartz 格式：``要查看更详细的选项，请输入自定义 Quartz 字符"
"串。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:26
msgid ""
"For example, to run a recurring action at 0215 every Saturday of every "
"month, enter:"
msgstr "例如，要在每个月的每个星期六 02:15 运行重复性操作，请输入："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "0 15 2 ? * 7\n"
msgstr "0 15 2 ? * 7\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:28
msgid ""
"OPTIONAL: Toggle the [guimenu]``Test mode`` switch on to run the schedule in "
"test mode."
msgstr ""
"可选：将[guimenu]``测试模式``开关切换为打开，以在测试模式下运行日程安排。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:29
msgid ""
"For actions of type [parameter]``Custom state``, select the states from the "
"list of available states and click btn:[Save Changes]. This will only save "
"the current state selection and not the schedule."
msgstr ""
"对于[parameter]``自定义状态``类型的操作，请从可用状态列表中选择状态，然后单"
"击 btn:[保存更改]。此操作只会保存当前选择的状态，而不会保存日程安排。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:30
msgid ""
"In the next pane, drag and drop the selected states to put them in the "
"execution order and click btn:[Confirm]."
msgstr "在下一个窗格中，拖放所选状态使其按执行顺序排列，然后单击 btn:[确认]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:31
msgid ""
"Finally, click btn:[Create Schedule] to save, and see the complete list of "
"existing schedules."
msgstr "最后，单击 btn:[创建日程安排] 保存设置，并查看现有日程安排的完整列表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:32
msgid ""
"Organization Administrators can set and edit recurring actions for all "
"clients in the organization.  Navigate to menu:Home[My Organization > "
"Recurring Actions] to see all recurring actions that apply to the entire "
"organization."
msgstr ""
"组织管理员可为组织中的所有客户端设置和编辑重复性操作。导航到menu:首页[我的组"
"织 > 重复性操作]，即可看到适用于整个组织的所有重复性操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:33
msgid ""
"{productname} Administrators can set and edit recurring actions for all "
"clients in all organizations.  Navigate to menu:Admin[Organizations], select "
"the organization to manage, and navigate to the menu:States[Recurring "
"Actions] tab."
msgstr ""
"{productname} 管理员可为所有组织中的所有客户端设置和编辑重复性操作。导航到"
"menu:管理[组织]，选择要管理的组织，然后导航到menu:状态[重复性操作]选项卡。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:34
msgid ""
"Recurring actions can only be used with Salt clients.  Traditional clients "
"in your group or organization are ignored."
msgstr "重复性操作只可用于 Salt 客户端。将忽略组或组织中的传统客户端。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Action Chains"
msgstr "操作链"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:36
msgid ""
"If you need to perform a number of sequential actions on your clients, you "
"can create an action chain to ensure the order is respected."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要对客户端执行多个有序操作，可以创建一个操作链以确保遵循该顺序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:37
msgid ""
"By default, most clients execute an action as soon as the command is "
"issued.  In some case, actions take a long time, which could mean that "
"actions issued afterwards fail.  For example, if you instruct a client to "
"reboot, then issue a second command, the second action could fail because "
"the reboot is still occurring.  To ensure that actions occur in the correct "
"order, use action chains."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，大多数客户端会在发出命令后立即执行操作。在某些情况下，操作需要很"
"长时间，这可能意味着之后发出的操作会失败。例如，如果您指示客户端重引导，然后"
"发出第二个命令，则第二个操作可能会失败，因为重引导仍在进行。为确保操作按正确"
"的顺序进行，请使用操作链。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:38
msgid ""
"For transactional update systems, an action chain is executed inside a "
"single snapshot, until there is a reboot action.  This can cause some "
"limitations."
msgstr ""
"对于事务更新系统，操作链会在单个快照内执行，直到进行重引导操作。这可能会产生"
"某些限制。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:39
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:73
msgid ""
"For more information, see xref:client-configuration:clients-slemicro.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息，请参见 xref:client-configuration:clients-slemicro.adoc[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:40
msgid ""
"You can use action chains on both traditional and Salt clients.  Action "
"chains can include any number of these actions, in any order:"
msgstr ""
"可以在传统客户端和 Salt 客户端上使用操作链。操作链可以包含任意数量、采用任意"
"顺序的以下操作："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:41
msgid "menu:System Details[Remote Command]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[远程命令]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:42
msgid "menu:System Details[Schedule System Reboot]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[安排系统重引导]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:43
msgid "menu:System Details[States > Highstate]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[状态 > Highstate]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:44
msgid "menu:System Details[Software > Packages > List/Remove]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[软件 > 软件包 > 列出/去除]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:45
msgid "menu:System Details[Software > Packages > Install]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[软件 > 软件包 > 安装]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:46
msgid "menu:System Details[Software > Packages > Upgrade]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[软件 > 软件包 > 升级]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:47
msgid "menu:System Details[Software > Patches]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[软件 > 补丁]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:48
msgid "menu:System Details[Software > Software Channels]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[软件 > 软件通道]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:49
msgid "menu:System Details[Configuration]"
msgstr "menu:系统细节[配置]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:50
msgid "menu:Images[Build]"
msgstr "menu:映像[构建]"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating a New Action Chain"
msgstr "过程：创建新操作链"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:52
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to the first action you want to "
"perform in the action chain.  For example, navigate to [guimenu]``System "
"Details`` for a client, and click btn:[Schedule System Reboot]."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，导航到您要在操作链中执行的第一个操作。例如，导航"
"到客户端的[guimenu]``系统细节``，然后单击 btn:[安排系统重引导]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:53
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Add to`` field and select the action chain you want to "
"add to:"
msgstr "选中[guimenu]``添加到``字段，然后选择要将操作添加到的操作链："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:54
msgid "If this is your first action chain, select ``new action chain``."
msgstr "如果这是您的第一个操作链，请选择``新建操作链``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:55
msgid "If the action chain already exists, select it from the list."
msgstr "如果该操作链已存在，请从列表中选择它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:56
msgid ""
"If you already have existing action chains, but you want to create a new "
"action chain, start typing a name for the new action chain to create it."
msgstr ""
"如果您已有操作链，但想要创建一个新操作链，请键入新操作链的名称以创建该操作"
"链。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:57
msgid "Confirm the action."
msgstr "确认操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:58
msgid ""
"The action is not performed immediately, it creates the new action chain, "
"and a blue bar confirming this appears at the top of the screen."
msgstr ""
"该操作不会立即执行，而是创建新的操作链，并在屏幕顶部显示一个确认此行为的蓝色"
"条。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:59
msgid ""
"Continue adding actions to your action chain by checking the [guimenu]``Add "
"to`` field and selecting the name of the action chain to add them to."
msgstr ""
"继续将操作添加到操作链，方法是选中[guimenu]``添加到``字段并选择要将操作添加到"
"的操作链的名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:60
msgid ""
"When you have finished adding actions, navigate to menu:Schedule[Action "
"Chains] and selecting the action chain from the list."
msgstr "添加完操作后，导航到menu:日程安排[操作链]并从列表中选择操作链。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:61
msgid ""
"Re-order actions by dragging them and dropping them into the correct "
"position."
msgstr "通过将操作拖放到正确的位置来重新排列操作顺序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:62
msgid ""
"Click the blue plus sign to see the clients an action is to be performed "
"on.  Click btn:[Save] to save your changes."
msgstr "单击蓝色加号查看要对其执行操作的客户端。单击 btn:[保存] 以保存更改。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:63
msgid ""
"Schedule a time for your action chain to run, and click btn:[Save and "
"Schedule]."
msgstr "安排操作链的运行时间，然后单击 btn:[保存并安排]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:64
msgid ""
"If you leave the page without clicking either btn:[Save] or btn:[Save and "
"Schedule] all unsaved changes are discarded."
msgstr ""
"如果您在不单击 btn:[保存] 或 btn:[保存并安排] 的情况下离开页面，将丢弃所有未"
"保存的更改。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:65
msgid ""
"If one action in an action chain fails, the action chain stops, and no "
"further actions are executed."
msgstr "如果操作链中的某个操作失败，操作链将会停止，且不再执行其他操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:66
msgid ""
"You can see scheduled actions from action chains by navigating to menu:"
"Schedule[Pending Actions]."
msgstr "可以通过导航到menu:日程安排[待执行的操作]来查看操作链中已安排的操作。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "Remote Commands"
msgstr "远程命令"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:68
msgid ""
"You can configure clients to run commands remotely.  This allows you to "
"issue scripts or individual commands to a client, without having access to "
"the client directly."
msgstr ""
"可以将客户端配置为远程运行命令。这样，在无法直接访问客户端的情况下，也可以向"
"客户端发出脚本或单个命令。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:69
msgid ""
"This feature is automatically enabled on Salt clients, and you do not need "
"to perform any further configuration.  For traditional clients, the feature "
"is enabled if you have registered the client using a bootstrap script and "
"have enabled remote commands.  You can use this procedure to enable it "
"manually, instead."
msgstr ""
"此功能在 Salt 客户端上已自动启用，您无需执行任何其他配置。对于传统客户端，如"
"果您已使用引导脚本注册客户端并已启用远程命令，则会启用该功能。您也可以使用以"
"下过程手动启用该功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:70
msgid ""
"Before you begin, ensure your client is subscribed to the appropriate tools "
"child channel for its installed operating system.  For more information "
"about subscribing to software channels, see xref:client-configuration:"
"channels.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"在开始之前，请确保您的客户端已订阅适用于其中所安装操作系统的工具子通道。有关"
"订阅软件通道的详细信息，请参见 xref:client-configuration:channels.adoc[]。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:71
msgid ""
"For transactional update systems, consider that a remote command is run "
"inside a single snapshot.  This can cause some limitations."
msgstr ""
"对于事务更新系统，需考虑到远程命令会在单个快照内运行。这可能会产生某些限制。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:72
msgid ""
"For more information, see xref:client-configuration:clients-slemicro.adoc[] "
"and xref:client-configuration:clients-microos.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息，请参见 xref:client-configuration:clients-slemicro.adoc[] 和 "
"xref:client-configuration:clients-microos.adoc[]。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Configuring Traditional Clients to Accept Remote Commands"
msgstr "过程：将传统客户端配置为接受远程命令"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:75
msgid ""
"On the client, at the command prompt, use the package manager to install the "
"[systemitem]``rhncfg``, [systemitem]``rhncfg-client``, and "
"[systemitem]``rhncfg-actions`` packages, if not already installed."
msgstr ""
"在客户端上的命令提示符下，使用软件包管理器安装 [systemitem]``rhncfg``、"
"[systemitem]``rhncfg-client`` 和 [systemitem]``rhncfg-actions`` 软件包（如果"
"尚未安装）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:76
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:130
#: modules/administration/pages/custom-channels.adoc:51
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:12
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:17
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:22
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-salt-clients-down-and-dns.adoc:9
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "zypper in rhncfg rhncfg-client rhncfg-actions\n"
msgstr "zypper in rhncfg rhncfg-client rhncfg-actions\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:78
msgid ""
"On the client, at the command prompt, as root, create a path in the local "
"configuration directory:"
msgstr "在客户端上的命令提示符下，以 root 身份在本地配置目录中创建一个路径："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:79
#, no-wrap
msgid "mkdir -p /etc/sysconfig/rhn/allowed-actions/script\n"
msgstr "mkdir -p /etc/sysconfig/rhn/allowed-actions/script\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:80
msgid "Create an empty file called [path]``run`` in the new directory."
msgstr "在新目录中创建名为 [path]``run`` 的空文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:81
msgid ""
"This file grants the {productname} Server permission to run remote commands:"
msgstr "此文件授予 {productname} Server 运行远程命令的权限："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "touch /etc/sysconfig/rhn/allowed-actions/script/run\n"
msgstr "touch /etc/sysconfig/rhn/allowed-actions/script/run\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:83
msgid ""
"For Salt clients, remote commands are run from the [path]``/tmp/`` directory "
"on the client.  To ensure that remote commands work accurately, do not mount "
"``/tmp`` with the [parameter]``noexec`` option.  For more information, see "
"xref:administration:troubleshooting/tshoot-intro.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"Salt 客户端是从其 [path]``/tmp`` 目录中运行远程命令。为确保远程命令准确执行，"
"请勿使用 [parameter]``noexec`` 选项挂载 ``/tmp``。有关详细信息，请参见 xref:"
"administration:troubleshooting/tshoot-intro.adoc[]。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:84
msgid ""
"All commands run from the [guimenu]``Remote Commands`` page are executed as "
"{rootuser} on clients.  Wildcards can be used to run commands across any "
"number of systems.  Always take extra care to check your commands before "
"issuing them."
msgstr ""
"从[guimenu]``远程命令``页面运行的所有命令将在客户端上以 {rootuser} 身份执行。"
"可以使用通配符在任意数量的系统上运行命令。请务必在仔细检查后再发出命令。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Running Remote Commands on Traditional Clients"
msgstr "过程：在传统客户端上运行远程命令"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/actions.adoc:86
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to [guimenu]``Systems``, click the "
"client to run a remote command on, and navigate to the menu:Details[Remote "
"Command] tab."
msgstr ""
