"Select the patch statuses you want to look for, or leave all statuses "
"checked to look for all."
msgstr "选择您要查看的补丁状态，或保持选中所有状态以查看所有补丁状态。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:19
msgid ""
"Click btn:[Audit Servers] to check all systems, or click btn:[Audit Images] "
"to check all images."
msgstr ""
"单击 btn:[审计服务器] 检查所有系统，或单击 btn:[审计映像] 检查所有映像。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:20
msgid ""
"For more information about the patch status icons used on this page, see "
"xref:reference:audit/audit-cve-audit.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关此页面上使用的补丁状态图标的详细信息，请参见 xref:reference:audit/audit-"
"cve-audit.adoc[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:21
msgid ""
"For each system, the [guimenu]``Next Action`` column provides information "
"about what you need to do to address vulnerabilities.  If applicable, a list "
"of candidate channels or patches is also given.  You can also assign systems "
"to a [guimenu]``System Set`` for further batch processing."
msgstr ""
"对于每个系统，[guimenu]``下一个操作``列会提供有关需要采取哪些措施才能解决漏洞"
"的信息。如果适用，其中还会列出候选通道或补丁。您还可以将系统指派到[guimenu]``"
"系统集``以做进一步的批处理。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:22
msgid ""
"You can use the {productname} API to verify the patch status of your "
"clients.  Use the ``audit.listSystemsByPatchStatus`` API method.  For more "
"information about this method, see the {productname} API Guide."
msgstr ""
"可以使用 {productname} API 来校验客户端的补丁状态。使用 ``audit."
"listSystemsByPatchStatus`` API 方法。有关此方法的详细信息，请参见"
"《{productname} API 指南》。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "CVE Status"
msgstr "CVE 状态"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:24
msgid ""
"The CVE status of clients is usually either ``affected``, ``not affected``, "
"or ``patched``.  These statuses are based only on the information that is "
"available to {productname}."
msgstr ""
"客户端的 CVE 状态通常是``受影响``、``不受影响``或``已增补``。这些状态仅取决"
"于 {productname} 适用的信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:25
msgid "Within {productname}, these definitions apply:"
msgstr "在 {productname} 中，以下定义适用："

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "System affected by a certain vulnerability"
msgstr "受特定漏洞影响的系统"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:27
msgid ""
"A system which has an installed package with version lower than the version "
"of the same package in a relevant patch marked for the vulnerability."
msgstr "系统中安装的某个软件包版本低于标记为漏洞的相关补丁中相同软件包的版本。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "System not affected by a certain vulnerability"
msgstr "不受特定漏洞影响的系统"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:29
msgid ""
"A system which has no installed package that is also in a relevant patch "
"marked for the vulnerability."
msgstr "同时包含在标记为漏洞的相关补丁中的软件包未安装在系统上。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "System patched for a certain vulnerability"
msgstr "针对某个漏洞进行了增补的系统"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:31
msgid ""
"A system which has an installed package with version equal to or greater "
"than the version of the same package in a relevant patch marked for the "
"vulnerability."
msgstr ""
"系统中安装的某个软件包版本等同于或高于标记为漏洞的相关补丁中相同软件包的版"
"本。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Relevant patch"
msgstr "相关补丁"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:33
msgid "A patch known by {productname} in a relevant channel."
msgstr "{productname} 在相关通道中已知的补丁。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Relevant channel"
msgstr "相关通道"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:35
msgid ""
"A channel managed by {productname}, which is either assigned to the system, "
"the original of a cloned channel which is assigned to the system, a channel "
"linked to a product which is installed on the system or a past or future "
"service pack channel for the system."
msgstr ""
"由 {productname} 管理的通道，该通道被指派到系统、是指派到系统的克隆通道的原始"
"通道、是链接到系统上安装的产品的通道，或者是系统的过去或将来的服务包通道。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/auditing.adoc:36
msgid ""
"Because of the definitions used within {productname}, CVE audit results "
"might be incorrect in some circumstances.  For example, unmanaged channels, "
"unmanaged packages, or non-compliant systems might report incorrectly."
msgstr ""
"由于 {productname} 中使用的定义，CVE 审计结果在某些情况下可能不正确。例如，非"
"受管通道、非受管软件包或不合规的系统可能会错误地报告结果。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Authentication With PAM"
msgstr "使用 PAM 进行身份验证"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:2
msgid ""
"{productname} supports network-based authentication systems using pluggable "
"authentication modules (PAM).  PAM is a suite of libraries that allows you "
"to integrate {productname} with a centralized authentication mechanism, "
"eliminating the need to remember multiple passwords.  {productname} supports "
"LDAP, Kerberos, and other network-based authentication systems using PAM."
msgstr ""
"{productname} 支持使用可插入身份验证模块 (PAM) 的基于网络的身份验证系统。PAM "
"是一个库套件，可用于将 {productname} 与集中式身份验证机制集成，从而无需记住多"
"个口令。{productname} 支持 LDAP、Kerberos 和其他使用 PAM 的基于网络的身份验证"
"系统。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Enabling PAM"
msgstr "过程：启用 PAM"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Create a PAM service file at [path]``/etc/pam.d/susemanager``.  Filename "
"must be in lower case and readable by ``tomcat`` user.  This file is used by "
"{productname} to load the correct PAM configuration files:"
msgstr ""
"在 [path]``/etc/pam.d/susemanager`` 中创建一个 PAM 服务文件。文件名必须采用小"
"写，并且可以由 ``tomcat`` 用户读取。{productname} 使用此文件来装载正确的 PAM "
"配置文件："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"#%PAM-1.0\n"
"auth     include        common-auth\n"
"account  include        common-account\n"
"password include        common-password\n"
"session  include        common-session\n"
msgstr ""
"#%PAM-1.0\n"
"auth     include        common-auth\n"
"account  include        common-account\n"
"password include        common-password\n"
"session  include        common-session\n"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid " On the {productname} Server, at the command prompt, as root, add the ``sss`` PAM module:"
msgstr " 在 {productname} Server 上的命令提示符下，以 root 身份添加 ``sss`` PAM 模块："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "pam-config -a --sss\n"
msgstr "pam-config -a --sss\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:8
msgid ""
"This command adds the module to the ``/etc/pam.d/common-auth`` configuration "
"file.  We do not recommend editing this file directly."
msgstr ""
"此命令将模块添加到 ``/etc/pam.d/common-auth`` 配置文件。我们不建议直接编辑此"
"文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Enforce the use of the service file by adding this line to [path]``/etc/rhn/"
"rhn.conf``:"
msgstr ""
"通过将下面一行内容添加到 [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` 来强制使用服务文件："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "pam_auth_service = susemanager\n"
msgstr "pam_auth_service = susemanager\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:11
msgid ""
"In this example, the PAM service file is called [systemitem]``susemanager``."
msgstr "在此示例中，PAM 服务文件名为 [systemitem]``susemanager``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:12
msgid "Restart the {productname} services after a configuration change."
msgstr "更改配置后重启动 {productname} 服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:13
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Users[Create User] and enable "
"a new or existing user to authenticate with PAM."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，导航到menu:用户[创建用户]，并允许新用户或现有用"
"户使用 PAM 进行身份验证。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Pluggable Authentication Modules (PAM)`` checkbox.  It "
"is below the password and password confirmation fields."
msgstr ""
"选中[guimenu]``可插入身份验证模块 (PAM)`` 复选框。该复选框位于口令和口令确认"
"字段下方。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:15
msgid ""
"Changing the password in the {productname} {webui} changes only the local "
"password on the {productname} Server.  If PAM is enabled for that user, the "
"local password might not be used at all.  In the above example, for "
"instance, the Kerberos password is not changed.  Use the password change "
"mechanism of your network service to change the password for these users."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中更改口令只会更改 {productname} Server 上的本地口"
"令。如果为该用户启用 PAM，则可能根本不会使用本地口令。例如，在上面的示例中，"
"Kerberos 口令并未更改。使用网络服务的口令更改机制来更改这些用户的口令。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:16
msgid ""
"To configure system-wide authentication you can use YaST.  You need to "
"install the [package]``yast2-auth-client`` package."
msgstr ""
"要配置系统范围的身份验证，可以使用 YaST。需要安装 [package]``yast2-auth-"
"client`` 软件包。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-pam.adoc:17
msgid ""
"For more information about configuring PAM, the SUSE Linux Enterprise Server "
"Security Guide contains a generic example that also works for other network-"
"based authentication methods.  It also describes how to configure an active "
"directory service.  For more information, see https://documentation.suse.com/"
"sles/15-SP3/html/SLES-all/part-auth.html."
msgstr ""
"有关配置 PAM 的详细信息，请参见《SUSE Linux Enterprise Server 安全指南》，其"
"中提供了一个通用示例，该示例同样适用于其他基于网络的身份验证方法。其中还介绍"
"了如何配置 Active Directory 服务。有关详细信息，请参见 link:https://"
"documentation.suse.com/sles/15-SP3/html/SLES-all/part-auth.html[]。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example SSO Implementation"
msgstr "示例 SSO 实现"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:2
msgid ""
"In this example, SSO is implemented by exposing three endpoints with "
"{productname}, and using Keycloak 21.0.1 or later as the identity service "
"provider (IdP)."
msgstr ""
"此示例通过使用 {productname} 公开三个端点并使用 Keycloak 21.0.1 或更高版本作"
"为身份服务提供者 (IdP) 来实现 SSO。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:3
msgid ""
"Start by installing the Keycloak IdP, then setting up the {productname} "
"Server.  Then you can add the endpoints as Keycloak clients, and create "
"users."
msgstr ""
"首先安装 Keycloak IdP，然后设置 {productname} 服务器。之后可以将端点添加为 "
"Keycloak 客户端并创建用户。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:4
msgid ""
"This example is provided for illustrative purposes only.  {suse} does not "
"recommend or support third-party identity service providers, and is not "
"affiliated with Keycloak.  For Keycloak support, see https://www.keycloak."
"org/."
msgstr ""
"此示例仅用于说明目的。{suse} 不建议也不支持第三方身份服务提供者，并且与 "
"Keycloak 不存在从属关系。有关 Keycloak 支持信息，请参见 link:https://www."
"keycloak.org/[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:5
msgid ""
"You can install Keycloak directly on your machine, or run it in a "
"container.  In this example, we run Keycloak in a Podman container.  For "
"more information about installing Keycloak, see the Keycloak documentation "
"at https://www.keycloak.org/guides#getting-started."
msgstr ""
"可以直接在您的计算机上安装 Keycloak，或者在容器中运行 Keycloak。此示例在 "
"Podman 容器中运行 Keycloak。有关安装 Keycloak 的详细信息，请参见 https://www."
"keycloak.org/guides#getting-started 上的 Keycloak 文档。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Setting Up the Identity Service Provider"
msgstr "过程：设置身份服务提供者"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:7
msgid ""
"Install Keycloak in a Podman container, according to the Keycloak "
"documentation."
msgstr "根据 Keycloak 文档所述在 Podman 容器中安装 Keycloak。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Run the container using the ``-td`` argument to ensure the process remains "
"running:"
msgstr "使用 ``-td`` 参数运行容器，以确保进程保持运行："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "podman run -td --name keycloak -p 8080:8080 -e KEYCLOAK_USER=admin -e KEYCLOAK_PASSWORD=admin quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:21.0.1\n"
msgstr "podman run -td --name keycloak -p 8080:8080 -e KEYCLOAK_USER=admin -e KEYCLOAK_PASSWORD=admin quay.io/keycloak/keycloak:21.0.1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Sign in the Keycloak {webui} as the ``admin`` user, and create an "
"authentication realm using these details:"
msgstr ""
"以 ``admin`` 用户身份登录到 Keycloak {webui}，然后使用以下细节创建身份验证领"
"域："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:11
msgid "In the ``Name`` field, enter a name for the realm."
msgstr "在``名称``字段中输入领域的名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:12
msgid "For example, ``SUMA``."
msgstr "例如 ``SUMA``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:13
msgid ""
"In the ``Endpoints`` field, click the ``SAML 2.0 Identity Provider "
"Metadata`` link."
msgstr "在``端点``字段中，单击 ``SAML 2.0 身份提供者元数据``链接。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:14
msgid ""
"This will lead you to a page where you will see the endpoints and "
"certificate to copy into the {productname} configuration file."
msgstr ""
"如此您将转到一个页面，其中会显示要复制到 {productname} 配置文件中的端点和证"
"书。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:15
msgid ""
"When you have installed Keycloak and created the realm, you can prepare the "
"{productname} Server."
msgstr "安装 Keycloak 并创建领域后，便可以准备 {productname} 服务器。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Setting Up the {productname} Server"
msgstr "过程：设置 {productname} Server"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:17
msgid ""
"On the {productname} Server, open the [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` "
"configuration file and edit these parameters."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} Server 上打开 [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` 配置文件，然后编辑"
"这些参数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Replace ``<FQDN_SUMA>`` with the fully qualified domain name of your "
"{productname} installation:"
msgstr "将 ``<FQDN_SUMA>`` 替换为您的 {productname} 安装的完全限定域名："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp.entityid                       = https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/metadata\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp.assertion_consumer_service.url = https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/acs\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp.single_logout_service.url      = https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/sls\n"
msgstr ""
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp.entityid                       = https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/metadata\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp.assertion_consumer_service.url = https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/acs\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp.single_logout_service.url      = https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/sls\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In the configuration file, replace ``<FQDN_IDP>`` with the fully qualified "
"domain name of your Keycloak server."
msgstr ""
"在配置文件中，将 ``<FQDN_IDP>`` 替换为您的 Keycloak 服务器的完全限定域名。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:21
msgid ""
"Replace ``<REALM>`` with your authentication realm, for example ``SUMA``:"
msgstr "将 ``<REALM>`` 替换为您的身份验证领域，例如 ``SUMA``："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:22
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.entityid                   = http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.single_sign_on_service.url = http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>/protocol/saml\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.single_logout_service.url  = http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>/protocol/saml\n"
msgstr ""
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.entityid                   = http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.single_sign_on_service.url = http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>/protocol/saml\n"
"java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.single_logout_service.url  = http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>/protocol/saml\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:23
msgid "In the IdP metadata, locate the public x509 certificate."
msgstr "在 IdP 元数据中，找到公共 x509 证书。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:24
msgid ""
"It uses this format: ``http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>/protocol/saml/"
"descriptor``.  In the configuration file, specify the public x509 "
"certificate of the IdP:"
msgstr ""
"证书使用如下格式：``http://<FQDN_IDP>:8080/realms/<REALM>/protocol/saml/"
"descriptor``。在配置文件中指定 IdP 的公共 x509 证书："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.x509cert = -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE----- <CERTIFICATE>  -----END CERTIFICATE-----\n"
msgstr "java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.x509cert = -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE----- <CERTIFICATE>  -----END CERTIFICATE-----\n"

