"您可以将 {productname} 端点添加到 Keycloak 中。Keycloak 将端点称为客户端。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Adding Endpoints as Clients"
