#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:39
msgid "In the Keycloak {webui}, create a new client using these details:"
msgstr "在 Keycloak {webui} 中，使用以下细节创建新客户端："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:40
msgid "In the ``Client type`` field, select ``SAML``."
