#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:41
msgid ""
"In the ``Client ID`` field, enter the endpoint specified in the server "
"configuration file as ``java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp.entityid``."
msgstr ""
"在``客户端 ID`` 字段中，输入服务器配置文件中以 ``java.sso.onelogin.saml2.idp."
"entityid`` 形式指定的端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:42
msgid "For example, ``https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/metadata``."
msgstr "例如 ``https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/metadata``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:43
msgid "In the ``Settings`` tab, fine-tune the client using these details:"
msgstr "在``设置``选项卡中，使用以下细节对客户端进行精细调整："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:44
msgid "Toggle the ``Sign assertions`` switch to ``On``."
msgstr "将``对声明签名``开关切换为``开``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:45
msgid "In the ``Signature algorithm`` field, select ``RSA_SHA1``."
msgstr "在``签名算法``字段中选择 ``RSA_SHA1``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:46
msgid "In the ``SAML Signature Key Name`` field, select ``Key ID``."
msgstr "在 ``SAML 签名密钥名称``字段中，选择``密钥 ID``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:47
msgid "In the ``Keys`` tab:"
msgstr "在``密钥``选项卡中："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:48
msgid "Set ``Client signature required`` to ``Off``."
msgstr "将``需要客户端签名``切换为``关``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:49
msgid ""
"In the ``Advanced`` tab, in the ``Fine Grain SAML Endpoint Configuration`` "
"section, add the two endpoints using these details:"
msgstr ""
"在``高级``选项卡上的``精细 SAML 端点配置``部分，使用以下细节添加两个端点："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:50
msgid ""
"In both the ``Assertion Consumer Service`` fields, enter the endpoint "
"specified in the server configuration file as ``java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp."
"assertion_consumer_service.url``."
msgstr ""
"在``声明使用者服务``字段中，输入服务器配置文件中以 ``java.sso.onelogin.saml2."
"sp.assertion_consumer_service.url`` 形式指定的端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:51
msgid "For example, ``https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/acs``."
msgstr "例如 ``https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/acs``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:52
msgid ""
"In both the ``Logout Service`` fields, enter the endpoint specified in the "
"server configuration file as ``java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp."
"single_logout_service.url``."
msgstr ""
"在``注销服务``字段中，输入服务器配置文件中以 ``java.sso.onelogin.saml2.sp."
"single_logout_service.url`` 形式指定的端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:53
msgid "For example, ``https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/sls``."
msgstr "例如 ``https://<FQDN_SUMA>/rhn/manager/sso/sls``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:54
msgid ""
"When you have added the endpoints as clients, you can configure the client "
"scope, and map the users between Keycloak and {productname}."
msgstr ""
"将端点添加为客户端后，可以配置客户端范围，并在 Keycloak 和 {productname} 之间"
"映射用户。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Configuring Client Scope and Mappers"
msgstr "过程：配置客户端范围和映射程序"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:56
msgid ""
"In the Keycloak {webui}, navigate to the menu:Clients[Client scopes] tab and "
"assign ``role_list`` as the default client scope."
msgstr ""
"在 Keycloak {webui} 中，导航到menu:客户端[客户端范围]选项卡，然后将 "
"``role_list`` 指定为默认客户端范围。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:57
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Client_scopes[Mappers] tab and add a mapper for user "
"attribute ``uid``, using the default values."
msgstr ""
"导航到menu:客户端范围[映射程序]选项卡，然后使用默认值添加用户属性 ``UID`` 的"
"映射程序。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:58
msgid "This SAML attribute is expected by {productname}."
msgstr "{productname} 需要此 SAML 属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:59
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Client_scopes[Mappers] and click on ``role_list`` "
"mapper. Set ``Single Role Attribute`` to ``On``."
msgstr ""
"导航到menu:客户端范围[映射程序]，然后单击 ``role_list`` 映射程序。将``单角色"
"属性``设置为``开``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:60
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Users[Admin] section and create an administrative user."
msgstr "导航到menu:用户[管理员]部分并创建一个管理用户。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:61
msgid "This user does not need to match the {productname} administrative user."
msgstr "此用户不需要与 {productname} 管理用户匹配。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:62
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Users[Role mappings] tab, add an attribute named "
"``uid`` with a value that matches the username of the {productname} "
"administrative user."
msgstr ""
"导航到menu:用户[角色映射]选项卡，使用与 {productname} 管理用户的用户名匹配的"
"值添加名为 ``UID`` 的属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:63
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:Users[Credentials] tab, and set the same password as "
"used by the {productname} administrative user."
msgstr ""
"导航到menu:用户[身份凭证]选项卡，设置 {productname} 管理用户所用的同一口令。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:64
msgid "Save your changes."
msgstr "保存更改。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/auth-methods-sso-example.adoc:65
msgid ""
"When you have completed the configuration, you can test that the "
"installation is working as expected.  Restart the {productname} Server to "
"pick up your changes, and navigate to the {productname} {webui}.  If your "
"installation is working correctly, you are redirected to the Keycloak SSO "
