"the location of the backup, it needs to restart your database before "
"performing the archive.  This results in a small amount of downtime.  "
"Regular database backups do not require any downtime."
msgstr ""
"首次运行 [command]``smdba`` 或者更改了备份位置时，需要先重启动数据库，然后再"
"执行存档。这会导致短暂的停机。定期数据库备份完全不需要停机。"

