#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:69
msgid ""
"Allocate permanent storage space for your backup.  This example uses a "
"directory located at [path]``/var/spacewalk/``.  This becomes a permanent "
"target for your backup, so ensure it remains accessible by your server at "
"all times."
msgstr ""
"为备份分配永久储存空间。此示例使用 [path]``/var/spacewalk/`` 中的目录。此目录"
"将成为备份的永久目标，因此请确保您的服务器始终可以访问此目录。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:70
msgid "In your backup location, create a directory for the backup:"
msgstr "在您的备份位置为备份创建一个目录："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:71
msgid "As root:"
msgstr "以 root 身份运行以下命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "install -d -o postgres -g postgres -m 700 /var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"
msgstr "install -d -o postgres -g postgres -m 700 /var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:73
msgid "Ensure you have the correct permissions set on the backup location:"
msgstr "确保您对备份位置拥有适当的权限："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "chown postgres:postgres /var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"
msgstr "chown postgres:postgres /var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:75
msgid ""
"To create a backup for the first time, run the [command]``smdba backup-hot`` "
"command with the [option]``enable`` option set.  This creates the backup in "
"the specified directory, and, if necessary, restart the database:"
msgstr ""
"首次创建备份时，请运行 [command]``smdba backup-hot`` 命令并设置 "
"[option]``enable`` 选项。这会在指定的目录中创建备份，并根据需要重启动数据库："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "smdba backup-hot --enable=on --backup-dir=/var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"
msgstr "smdba backup-hot --enable=on --backup-dir=/var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:77
msgid ""
"This command produces debug messages and finishes sucessfully with the "
"output:"
msgstr "此命令将生成调试消息，成功完成时会返回以下输出："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "INFO: Finished\n"
msgstr "INFO: Finished\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:79
msgid ""
"Check that the backup files exist in the [path]``/var/spacewalk/db-backup`` "
"directory, to ensure that your backup has been successful."
msgstr ""
"检查 [path]``/var/spacewalk/db-backup`` 目录中是否存在备份文件，确保备份成"
"功。"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scheduling Automatic Backups"
msgstr "安排自动备份"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:81
msgid ""
"You do not need to shut down your system to perform a database backup with "
"[command]``smdba``.  However, because it is a large operation, database "
"performance can slow down while the backup is running.  We recommend you "
"schedule regular database backups for a low-traffic period, to minimize "
"disruption."
msgstr ""
"无需关闭系统即可使用 [command]``smdba`` 执行数据库备份。但是，由于备份是一项"
"大规模操作，因此在运行备份时，数据库性能可能会下降。我们建议您将定期数据库备"
"份安排在低流量时段，以尽量减少中断。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:82
msgid ""
"Ensure you have at least three times the current database size of space "
"available for backups.  You can check your current database size by "
"navigating to [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/`` and running [command]``df -h``."
msgstr ""
"请确保至少提供当前数据库大小三倍的可用空间用于备份。可以通过导航到 [path]``/"
"var/lib/pgsql/`` 并运行 [command]``df -h`` 来检查当前数据库大小。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Scheduling Automatic Backups"
msgstr "过程：安排自动备份"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:84
msgid ""
"Create a directory for the backup, and set the appropriate permissions (as "
"root):"
msgstr "为备份创建一个目录并设置适当的权限（以 root 身份）："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "install -m 700 -o postgres -g postgres /var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"
msgstr "install -m 700 -o postgres -g postgres /var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:86
msgid ""
"Open [path]``/etc/cron.d/db-backup-mgr``, or create it if it does not exist, "
"and add the following line to create the cron job:"
msgstr ""
"打开 [path]``/etc/cron.d/db-backup-mgr``（如果该文件不存在，请创建），并在其"
"中添加下面一行内容以创建 cron 作业："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:87
#, no-wrap
msgid "0 2 * * * root /usr/bin/smdba backup-hot --enable=on --backup-dir=/var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"
msgstr "0 2 * * * root /usr/bin/smdba backup-hot --enable=on --backup-dir=/var/spacewalk/db-backup\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:88
msgid ""
"Check the backup directory regularly to ensure the backups are working as "
"expected."
msgstr "定期检查备份目录以确保备份按预期进行。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Restore from Backup"
msgstr "从备份中还原"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:90
msgid ""
"The [command]``smdba`` tool can be used to restore from backup in the case "
"of failure."
msgstr "发生故障时，可以使用 [command]``smdba`` 工具从备份中还原。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Restoring from Backup"
msgstr "过程：从备份中还原"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:92
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:150
msgid "Shut down the database:"
msgstr "关闭数据库："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:94
msgid "Start the restore process and wait for it to complete:"
msgstr "启动还原过程并等待它完成："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "smdba backup-restore start\n"
msgstr "smdba backup-restore start\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:96
msgid "Restart the database:"
msgstr "重启动数据库："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:98
msgid "Check if there are differences between the RPMs and the database."
msgstr "检查 RPM 和数据库之间是否有差异。"

