#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:108
msgid ""
"PostgreSQL generates an additional roughly 1 GB of data.  So it is important "
"to think about a backup strategy and create a backups in a regular way."
msgstr ""
"PostgreSQL 会额外生成大约 1 GB 数据。因此，请务必考虑备份策略并定期创建备份。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:109
msgid ""
"Archive logs are stored at [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/data/pg_xlog/`` "
"(postgresql)."
msgstr ""
"存档日志储存在 [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/data/pg_xlog/`` (postgresql) 中。"

