#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Move the Database"
msgstr "移动数据库"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:122
msgid ""
"It is possible to move the database to another location.  For example, if "
"database storage space is running low."
msgstr "可以将数据库移到另一个位置。例如，在数据库储存空间不足的情况下。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Moving the Database"
msgstr "过程：移动数据库"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:124
msgid ""
"The default storage location for {productname} is [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/``. "
"If you would like to move it, for example to [path]``/storage/postgres/``, "
"proceed as follows."
msgstr ""
"{productname} 的默认储存位置是 [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/``。如果您想要移动此位"
"置，例如移到 [path]``/storage/postgres/``，请执行以下操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:125
msgid "At the command prompt, as root, stop the running database:"
msgstr "在命令提示符下，以 root 身份停止正在运行的数据库："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:126
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "rcpostgresql stop\n"
msgstr "rcpostgresql stop\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:127
msgid "Shut down the running spacewalk services:"
msgstr "关闭正在运行的 spacewalk 服务："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:128
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:153
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-logintimeout.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacewalk-service stop\n"
msgstr "spacewalk-service stop\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:129
msgid ""
"Copy the current working directory structure with [command]``cp`` using the "
"[option]``-a, --archive`` option."
msgstr ""
"结合 [option]``-a、--archive`` 选项使用 [command]``cp`` 复制当前工作目录结"
"构。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:131
#, no-wrap
msgid "cp --archive /var/lib/pgsql/ /storage/postgres/\n"
msgstr "cp --archive /var/lib/pgsql/ /storage/postgres/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:132
msgid ""
"This command copies the contents of [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/`` to [path]``/"
"storage/postgres/pgsql/``."
msgstr ""
"此命令将 [path]``/var/lib/pgsql/`` 的内容复制到 [path]``/storage/postgres/"
"pgsql/``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:133
msgid ""
"The contents of the [path]``/var/lib/pgsql`` directory needs to remain the "
"same, otherwise the {productname} database may malfunction.  You also should "
"ensure that there is enough available disk space."
msgstr ""
"[path]``/var/lib/pgsql`` 目录的内容需保持不变，否则 {productname} 数据库可能"
"会出现异常。您还应该确保有足够的可用磁盘空间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:134
msgid "Mount the new database directory:"
msgstr "挂载新的数据库目录："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "mount /storage/postgres/pgsql\n"
msgstr "mount /storage/postgres/pgsql\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:136
msgid ""
"Make sure ownership is `postgres:postgres` and not `root:root` by changing "
"to the new directory and running these commands:"
msgstr ""
"切换到新目录并运行以下命令，确保所有权是 `postgres:postgres` 而不是 `root:"
"root`："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/backup-restore.adoc:137
