#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:34
msgid ""
"SMT is included with {sle} 12, and can be used to manage clients running "
"{sle} 10 or later."
msgstr "SMT 已随附在 {sle} 12 中，可用于管理运行 {sle} 10 或更高版本的客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:35
msgid ""
"SMT requires you to create a local mirror directory on the SMT instance to "
"synchronize repositories and packages."
msgstr "SMT 要求您在 SMT 实例上创建一个本地镜像目录以同步储存库和软件包。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:36
msgid ""
"For more details on installing and configuring SMT, see https://"
"documentation.suse.com/sles/12-SP5/html/SLES-all/book-smt.html."
msgstr ""
"有关安装和配置 SMT 的更多细节，请参见 link:https://documentation.suse.com/"
"sles/12-SP5/html/SLES-all/book-smt.html[]。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:37
