"html#smt-mirroring-manage-domirror"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "Synchronize a Disconnected Server"
msgstr "同步已断开连接的服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:60
msgid ""
"When you have removable media loaded with your {scc} data, you can use it to "
"synchronize your disconnected server."
msgstr ""
"如果您有装载了 {scc} 数据的可卸媒体，可以使用它来同步已断开连接的服务器。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:61
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Synchronizing a Disconnected Server"
msgstr "过程：同步已断开连接的服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:62
msgid "Mount your removable media device to the {productname} server."
msgstr "将可卸媒体设备挂载到 {productname} 服务器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:63
msgid "In this example, the mount point is [path]``/media/disk``."
msgstr "在此例子中，挂载点是 [path]``/media/disk``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:64
msgid ""
"Open ``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` and define the mount point by adding or editing "
"this line:"
msgstr "打开 ``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf``，并通过添加或编辑下面一行内容来定义挂载点："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "server.susemanager.fromdir = /media/disk\n"
msgstr "server.susemanager.fromdir = /media/disk\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:66
msgid "Restart the Tomcat service:"
msgstr "重启动 Tomcat 服务："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "systemctl restart tomcat\n"
msgstr "systemctl restart tomcat\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:68
msgid "Refresh the local data:"
msgstr "刷新本地数据："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-sync refresh\n"
msgstr "mgr-sync refresh\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:70
msgid "Perform a synchronization:"
msgstr "执行同步："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:71
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"mgr-sync list channels\n"
"mgr-sync add channel channel-label\n"
msgstr ""
"mgr-sync list channels\n"
"mgr-sync add channel channel-label\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/disconnected-setup.adoc:72
msgid ""
"The removable disk that you use for synchronization must always be available "
"at the same mount point.  Do not trigger a synchronization, if the storage "
"medium is not mounted.  This results in data corruption."
msgstr ""
"用于同步的可御磁盘必须始终在同一挂载点上可用。如果未挂载储存媒体，请不要触发"
"同步，否则会导致数据损坏。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Image Building and Management"
msgstr "映像构建和管理"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Image Building Overview"
msgstr "映像构建概述"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:3
msgid ""
"{productname} enables system administrators to build containers and OS "
"Images and push the result in image stores.  The workflow looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"{productname} 允许系统管理员构建容器和操作系统映像，并将结果推送到映像储存。"
"工作流程如下："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:4
msgid "Define an image store"
msgstr "定义映像储存"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:5
msgid ""
"Define an image profile and associate it with a source (either a git "
"repository or a directory)"
msgstr "定义一个映像配置文件并将其与源（git 储存库或目录）相关联"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:6
msgid "Build the image"
msgstr "构建映像"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:7
msgid "Push the image to the image store"
msgstr "将映像推送到映像储存"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:8
msgid ""
"{productname} supports two distinct build types: dockerfile, and the Kiwi "
"image system."
msgstr "{productname} 支持两种不同的构建类型：dockerfile 和 Kiwi 映像系统。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:9
msgid ""
"The Kiwi build type is used to build system, virtual, and other images.  The "
"image store for the Kiwi build type is pre-defined as a file system "
"directory at [path]``/srv/www/os-images`` on the server.  {productname} "
"serves the image store over HTTPS from [literal]``//<SERVER-FQDN>/os-images/"
"``.  The image store location is unique and is not customizable."
msgstr ""
"Kiwi 构建类型用于构建系统映像、虚拟映像和其他映像。Kiwi 构建类型的映像储存预"
"定义为文件系统目录，其路径为服务器上的 [path]``/srv/www/os-images``。"
"{productname} 通过 HTTPS 从 [literal]``//<服务器 FQDN>/os-images/`` 提供映像"
"储存。映像储存位置是唯一的，不可自定义。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Images are always stored in [path]``/srv/www/os-image/<organization id>``."
msgstr "映像始终储存在 [path]``/srv/www/os-image/<组织 ID>`` 中。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Container Images"
msgstr "容器映像"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "image-building.png"
msgstr "image-building.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:14
msgid ""
"The containers feature is available for Salt clients running {sles} 12 or "
"later.  Before you begin, ensure your environment meets these requirements:"
msgstr ""
"容器功能适用于运行 {sles} 12 或更高版本的 Salt 客户端。在开始之前，请确保您的"
"环境满足以下要求："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:15
msgid ""
"A published git repository containing a dockerfile and configuration "
"scripts.  The repository can be public or private, and should be hosted on "
"GitHub, GitLab, or BitBucket."
msgstr ""
"一个包含 dockerfile 和配置脚本的已发布 git 储存库。该储存库可以是公用或专用"
"的，应托管在 GitHub、GitLab 或 BitBucket 上。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:16
msgid "A properly configured image store, such as a Docker registry."
msgstr "一个正确配置的映像储存，例如 Docker 注册表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:17
msgid "For more information on Containers, see:"
msgstr "有关容器的详细信息，请参见："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:18
msgid ""
"https://documentation.suse.com/sles/15-SP3/html/SLES-all/book-container.html"
msgstr ""
"https://documentation.suse.com/sles/15-SP3/html/SLES-all/book-container.html"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:19
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create a Build Host"
msgstr "创建构建主机"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:20
msgid ""
"To build images with {productname}, you need to create and configure a build "
"host.  Container build hosts are Salt clients running {sle} 12 or later.  "
"This section guides you through the initial configuration for a build host."
msgstr ""
"要使用 {productname} 构建映像，您需要创建并配置一个构建主机。容器构建主机是运"
"行 {sle} 12 或更高版本的 Salt 客户端。本节将指导您完成构建主机的初始配置。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:21
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:146
msgid ""
"The operating system on the build host must match the operating system on "
"the targeted image."
msgstr "构建主机上的操作系统必须与目标映像上的操作系统匹配。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:22
msgid ""
"For example, build {sles}{nbsp}15 based images on a build host running {sles}"
"{nbsp}15 (SP2 or later) OS version.  Build {sles}{nbsp}12 based images on a "
"build host running {sles}{nbsp}12 SP4 or {sles}{nbsp}12 SP3 OS version."
msgstr ""
"例如，在运行 {sles}{nbsp}15（SP2 或更高版本）操作系统版本的构建主机上构建基"
"于 {sles}{nbsp}15 的映像。在运行 {sles}{nbsp}12 SP4 或 {sles}{nbsp}12 SP3 操"
"作系统版本的构建主机上构建基于 {sles}{nbsp}12 的映像。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:23
msgid "Cross-architecture builds are not supported."
msgstr "不支持跨体系结构构建。"

#. 2022-05-12, ke: at least for now, according to feedback, this is unsupported:
#. For example, you must build Raspberry Pi {sles}{nbsp}15 SP3 images on a Raspberry Pi (aarch64 architecture) build host running {sles}{nbsp}15 SP3.
#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:24
msgid ""
"From the {productname} {webui}, perform these steps to configure a build "
"host:"
msgstr "在 {productname} {webui} 中，执行以下步骤以配置构建主机："

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Select a Salt client to be designated as a build host from the menu:"
"Systems[Overview] page."
msgstr "在menu:系统[概览]页面中选择要指定为构建主机的 Salt 客户端。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:26
msgid ""
"From the [guimenu]``System Details`` page of the selected client assign the "
"containers modules.  Go to menu:Software[Software Channels] and enable the "
"containers module (for example, [guimenu]``SLE-Module-Containers15-Pool`` "
"and [guimenu]``SLE-Module-Containers15-Updates``).  Confirm by clicking btn:"
"[Change Subscriptions]."
msgstr ""
"在所选客户端的[guimenu]``系统细节``页面中指派容器模块。转到menu:软件[软件通"
"道]并启用容器模块（例如 [guimenu]``SLE-Module-Containers15-Pool`` 和 "
"[guimenu]``SLE-Module-Containers15-Updates``）。单击 btn:[更改订阅] 以确认。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:27
msgid ""
"From the menu:System Details[Properties] page, enable ``Container Build "
"Host`` from the [guimenu]``Add-on System Types`` list and confirm by "
"clicking btn:[Update Properties]."
msgstr ""
"在menu:系统细节[属性]页面中，从[guimenu]``附加系统类型``列表中启用``容器构建"
"主机``，然后单击 btn:[更新属性] 以确认。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Install all required packages by applying ``Highstate``.  From the system "
"details page select menu:States[Highstate] and click [guimenu]``Apply "
"Highstate``.  Alternatively, apply Highstate from the {productname} Server "
"command line:"
msgstr ""
"通过应用 ``Highstate`` 安装所有必需的软件包。在系统细节页面中选择menu:状态"
"[Highstate]，然后单击[guimenu]``应用 Highstate``。或者，从 {productname} "
"Server 命令行应用 Highstate："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:29
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:158
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt '$your_client' state.highstate\n"
msgstr "salt '$your_client' state.highstate\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create an Activation Key for Containers"
msgstr "为容器创建激活密钥"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:31
msgid ""
"The containers built using {productname} use channels associated to the "
"activation key as repositories when building the image.  This section guides "
"you through creating an ad-hoc activation key for this purpose."
msgstr ""
"使用 {productname} 构建的容器使用在构建映像时作为储存库关联到激活密钥的通道。"
"本节将指导您为此目的创建一个临时激活密钥。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:32
msgid ""
"To build a container, you need an activation key that is associated with a "
"channel other than `SUSE Manager Default`."
msgstr ""
"要构建容器，需要一个与通道关联的激活密钥，但该通道不能是 ``SUSE Manager "
"Default``。"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:33
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:176
#, no-wrap
msgid "systems_create_activation_key.png"
msgstr "systems_create_activation_key.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:34
