#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:43
msgid "Click [guimenu]``Create`` to create a new store."
msgstr "单击[guimenu]``创建``以创建新储存。"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:44
