#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:59
msgid "Use a dockerfile as the `Image Type`."
msgstr "使用 dockerfile 作为``映像类型``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:60
msgid ""
"Use the drop-down menu to select your registry from the `Target Image Store` "
"field."
msgstr "使用下拉菜单从``目标映像储存``字段中选择您的注册表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:61
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Path`` field, type a GitHub, GitLab or BitBucket "
"repository URL.  The URL should be be http, https, or a token authentication "
"URL.  Use one of these formats:"
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``路径``字段中，键入 GitHub、GitLab 或 BitBucket 储存库 URL。该 "
"URL 应该是 http、https 或令牌身份验证 URL。使用以下格式之一："

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "GitHub Path Options"
msgstr "GitHub 路径选项"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:63
msgid "GitHub single user project repository"
msgstr "GitHub 单用户项目储存库"

#. type: delimited block -
