msgstr "https://github.com/USER/project.git#branchname:folder\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:65
msgid "GitHub organization project repository"
msgstr "GitHub 组织项目储存库"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://github.com/ORG/project.git#branchname:folder\n"
msgstr "https://github.com/ORG/project.git#branchname:folder\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:67
msgid "GitHub token authentication"
msgstr "GitHub 令牌身份验证"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:68
msgid ""
"If your git repository is private, modify the profile's URL to include "
"authentication.  Use this URL format to authenticate with a GitHub token:"
msgstr ""
"如果您的 git 储存库是专用的，请修改配置文件的 URL 以包含身份验证。使用以下 "
"URL 格式通过 GitHub 令牌进行身份验证："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://USER:<AUTHENTICATION_TOKEN>@github.com/USER/project.git#master:/container/\n"
msgstr "https://USER:<身份验证令牌>@github.com/USER/project.git#master:/container/\n"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "GitLab Path Options"
msgstr "GitLab 路径选项"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:71
msgid "GitLab single user project repository"
msgstr "GitLab 单用户项目储存库"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://gitlab.example.com/USER/project.git#master:/container/\n"
msgstr "https://gitlab.example.com/USER/project.git#master:/container/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:73
msgid "GitLab groups project repository"
msgstr "GitLab 组项目储存库"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://gitlab.example.com/GROUP/project.git#master:/container/\n"
msgstr "https://gitlab.example.com/GROUP/project.git#master:/container/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:75
msgid "GitLab token authentication"
msgstr "GitLab 令牌身份验证"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:76
msgid ""
"If your git repository is private and not publicly accessible, you need to "
"modify the profile's git URL to include authentication.  Use this URL format "
"to authenticate with a GitLab token:"
msgstr ""
"如果您的 git 储存库是专用的且不可公开访问，则需要修改配置文件的 git URL 以包"
"含身份验证。使用以下 URL 格式通过 GitLab 令牌进行身份验证："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://gitlab-ci-token:<AUTHENTICATION_TOKEN>@gitlab.example.com/USER/project.git#master:/container/\n"
msgstr "https://gitlab-ci-token:<身份验证令牌>@gitlab.example.com/USER/project.git#master:/container/\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:78
msgid ""
"If you do not specify a git branch, the `master` branch is used by default.  "
"If a `folder` is not specified, the image sources (dockerfile sources) are "
"expected to be in the root directory of the GitHub or GitLab checkout."
msgstr ""
"如果您未指定 git 分支，则默认会使用 `master` 分支。如果未指定 `folder`，则映"
"像源（dockerfile 源）预期位于 GitHub 或 GitLab checkout 分支的根目录中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:79
msgid ""
"Select an `Activation Key`.  Activation keys ensure that images using a "
"profile are assigned to the correct channel and packages."
msgstr ""
"选择一个``激活密钥``。激活密钥可确保将使用配置文件的映像指派到正确的通道和软"
"件包。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:80
msgid ""
"When you associate an activation key with an image profile you are ensuring "
"any image using the profile uses the correct software channel and any "
"packages in the channel."
msgstr ""
"将激活密钥与映像配置文件关联后，可以确保使用该配置文件的任何映像都会使用正确"
"的软件通道以及该通道中的任何软件包。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:81
msgid "Click the btn:[Create] button."
msgstr "单击 btn:[创建] 按钮。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Example Dockerfile Sources"
msgstr "示例 Dockerfile 源"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:83
msgid ""
"An Image Profile that can be reused is published at https://github.com/SUSE/"
"manager-build-profiles"
msgstr ""
"https://github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles 上发布了可重复使用的映像配置文"
"件"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:84
msgid ""
"The [option]``ARG`` parameters ensure that the built image is associated "
"with the desired repository served by {productname}.  The [option]``ARG`` "
"parameters also allow you to build image versions of {sles} which may differ "
"from the version of {sles} used by the build host itself."
msgstr ""
"[option]``ARG`` 参数确保构建的映像与 {productname} 提供的所需储存库相关联。"
"[option]``ARG`` 参数还可用于构建不同于构建主机本身所用 {sles} 版本的 {sles} "
"映像版本。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:85
msgid ""
"For example: The [command]``ARG repo`` parameter and the [command]``echo`` "
"command pointing to the repository file, creates and then injects the "
"correct path into the repository file for the desired channel version."
msgstr ""
"例如：[command]``ARG repo`` 参数以及指向储存库文件的 [command]``echo`` 命令创"
"建正确的路径，然后将其注入到所需通道版本的储存库文件中。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:86
msgid ""
"The repository is determined by the activation key that you assigned to your "
"image profile."
msgstr "储存库由您指派到映像配置文件的激活密钥决定。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:87
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"FROM registry.example.com/sles12sp2\n"
"MAINTAINER Tux Administrator \"tux@example.com\"\n"
msgstr ""
"FROM registry.example.com/sles12sp2\n"
"MAINTAINER Tux Administrator \"tux@example.com\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "### Begin: These lines Required for use with {productname}\n"
msgstr "### 开始：这些行需要与 {productname} 配合使用\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:89
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"ARG repo\n"
"ARG cert\n"
msgstr ""
"ARG repo\n"
"ARG cert\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:90
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Add the correct certificate\n"
"RUN echo \"$cert\" > /etc/pki/trust/anchors/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT.pem\n"
msgstr ""
"# 添加正确的证书\n"
"RUN echo \"$cert\" > /etc/pki/trust/anchors/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT.pem\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:91
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Update certificate trust store\n"
"RUN update-ca-certificates\n"
msgstr ""
"# 更新证书信任储存\n"
"RUN update-ca-certificates\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:92
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Add the repository path to the image\n"
"RUN echo \"$repo\" > /etc/zypp/repos.d/susemanager:dockerbuild.repo\n"
msgstr ""
"# 将储存库路径添加到映像\n"
"RUN echo \"$repo\" > /etc/zypp/repos.d/susemanager:dockerbuild.repo\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:93
#, no-wrap
msgid "### End: These lines required for use with {productname}\n"
msgstr "### 结束：这些行需要与 {productname} 配合使用\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:94
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Add the package script\n"
"ADD add_packages.sh /root/add_packages.sh\n"
msgstr ""
"# 添加打包脚本\n"
"ADD add_packages.sh /root/add_packages.sh\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:95
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# Run the package script\n"
"RUN /root/add_packages.sh\n"
msgstr ""
"# 运行打包脚本\n"
"RUN /root/add_packages.sh\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:96
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# After building remove the repository path from image\n"
"RUN rm -f /etc/zypp/repos.d/susemanager:dockerbuild.repo\n"
msgstr ""
"# 构建后从映像中去除储存库路径\n"
"RUN rm -f /etc/zypp/repos.d/susemanager:dockerbuild.repo\n"

