msgid "OS Images"
msgstr "操作系统映像"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:132
msgid ""
"OS Images are built by the Kiwi image system.  The output image is "
"customizable and can be PXE, QCOW2, LiveCD, or other types of images."
msgstr ""
"操作系统映像由 Kiwi 映像系统构建。输出映像可自定义，可以是 PXE、QCOW2、"
"LiveCD 或其他类型的映像。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:133
msgid ""
"For more information about the Kiwi build system, see the https://doc."
"opensuse.org/projects/kiwi/doc/[Kiwi documentation]."
msgstr ""
"有关 Kiwi 构建系统的详细信息，请参见 https://doc.opensuse.org/projects/kiwi/"
"doc/[Kiwi 文档]。"

#. SLE15 images support is not yet released for SUMA4, but is part of SUMA4.0.4 as tech preview
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:135
msgid ""
"The Kiwi image building feature is available for Salt clients running {sles}"
"{nbsp}12 and {sles}{nbsp}11."
msgstr ""
"Kiwi 映像构建功能适用于运行 {sles}{nbsp}12 和 {sles}{nbsp}11 的 Salt 客户端。"

#. From {sles}{nbsp}15, ``kiwi-ng`` is used instead of the legacy Kiwi.
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:136
msgid ""
"Kiwi image configuration files and configuration scripts must be accessible "
"in one of these locations:"
msgstr "必须可在以下位置之一访问 Kiwi 映像配置文件和配置脚本："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:137
msgid "Git repository"
msgstr "Git 储存库"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:138
msgid "HTTP hosted tarball"
msgstr "HTTP 托管 tarball"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:139
msgid "Local build host directory"
msgstr "本地构建主机目录"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:140
msgid ""
"For an example of a complete Kiwi repository served by git, see https://"
"github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles/tree/master/OSImage"
msgstr ""
"有关 git 提供的完整 Kiwi 储存库的示例，请参见 https://github.com/SUSE/"
"manager-build-profiles/tree/master/OSImage"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:141
msgid ""
"You need at least 1{nbsp}GB of RAM available for hosts running OS Images "
"built with Kiwi.  Disk space depends on the actual size of the image.  For "
"more information, see the documentation of the underlying system."
msgstr ""
"对于运行使用 Kiwi 构建的操作系统映像的主机，至少需要提供 1{nbsp}GB RAM。具体"
"所需磁盘空间取决于映像的实际大小。有关详细信息，请参见底层系统的文档。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:142
msgid ""
"The build host must be a Salt client.  Do not install the build host as a "
"traditional client."
msgstr "构建主机必须是 Salt 客户端。不要将构建主机作为传统客户端安装。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:144
msgid ""
"To build all kinds of images with {productname}, create and configure a "
"build host.  OS Image build hosts are Salt clients running on {sles}{nbsp}15 "
"(SP2 or later), {sles}{nbsp}12 (SP3 or later) or {sles}{nbsp}11 SP4."
msgstr ""
"要使用 {productname} 构建各种映像，请创建并配置一个构建主机。操作系统映像构建"
"主机是在 {sles}{nbsp}15（SP2 或更高版本）、{sles}{nbsp}12（SP3 或更高版本）"
"或 {sles}{nbsp}11 SP4 上运行的 Salt 客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:145
msgid ""
"This procedure guides you through the initial configuration for a build host."
msgstr "此过程将指导您完成构建主机的初始配置。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:147
msgid ""
"For example, build {sles}{nbsp}15 based images on a build host running {sles}"
"{nbsp}15 (SP2 or later) OS version.  Build {sles}{nbsp}12 based images on a "
"build host running {sles}{nbsp}12 SP4 or {sles}{nbsp}12 SP3 OS version.  "
"Build {sles}{nbsp}11 based images on a build host running {sles}{nbsp}11 SP4 "
"OS version."
msgstr ""
"例如，在运行 {sles}{nbsp}15（SP2 或更高版本）操作系统版本的构建主机上构建基"
"于 {sles}{nbsp}15 的映像。在运行 {sles}{nbsp}12 SP4 或 {sles}{nbsp}12 SP3 操"
"作系统版本的构建主机上构建基于 {sles}{nbsp}12 的映像。在运行 {sles}{nbsp}11 "
"SP4 操作系统版本的构建主机上构建基于 {sles}{nbsp}11 的映像。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:148
msgid ""
"Cross-architecture builds are not possible.  For example, you must build "
"Raspberry PI {sles}{nbsp}15 SP3 image on a Raspberry PI (aarch64 "
"architecture) build host running {sles}{nbsp}15 SP3."
msgstr ""
"无法实现跨体系结构的构建。例如，必须在运行 {sles}{nbsp}15 SP3 的 Raspberry PI"
"（aarch64 体系结构）构建主机上构建 Raspberry PI {sles}{nbsp}15 SP3 映像。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:149
msgid "Configure the build host in the {productname} {webui}:"
msgstr "在 {productname} {webui} 中配置构建主机："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:150
msgid ""
"Select a client to be designated as a build host from the menu:"
"Systems[Overview] page."
msgstr "在menu:系统[概览]页面中选择要指定为构建主机的客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:151
msgid ""
"Navigate to the menu:System Details[Properties] tab, enable the "
"[guimenu]``Add-on System Type`` [guimenu]``OS Image Build Host``. Confirm "
"with btn:[Update Properties]."
msgstr ""
"导航到menu:系统细节[属性]选项卡，为[guimenu]``附加系统类型``启用[guimenu]``操"
"作系统映像构建主机``。选择 btn:[更新属性] 以确认。"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:152
#, no-wrap
msgid "os-image-build-host.png"
msgstr "os-image-build-host.png"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:153
msgid ""
"Navigate to menu:System Details[Software > Software Channels], and enable "
"the required software channels depending on the build host version."
msgstr ""
"导航到menu:系统细节[软件 > 软件通道]，根据构建主机版本启用所需的软件通道。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:154
msgid ""
"{sles}{nbsp}11 build hosts require {productname} Client tools (``SLE-Manager-"
"Tools11-Pool`` and ``SLE-Manager-Tools11-Updates``)."
msgstr ""
"{sles}{nbsp}11 构建主机需要 {productname} 客户端工具（``SLE-Manager-Tools11-"
"Pool`` 和 ``SLE-Manager-Tools11-Updates``）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:155
msgid ""
"{sles}{nbsp}12 build hosts require {productname} Client tools (``SLE-Manager-"
"Tools12-Pool`` and ``SLE-Manager-Tools12-Updates``)."
msgstr ""
"{sles}{nbsp}12 构建主机需要 {productname} 客户端工具（``SLE-Manager-Tools12-"
"Pool`` 和 ``SLE-Manager-Tools12-Updates``）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:156
msgid ""
"{sles}{nbsp}15 build hosts require {sles} modules ``SLE-Module-DevTools15-"
"SP2-Pool`` and ``SLE-Module-DevTools15-SP2-Updates``.  Schedule and click "
"btn:[Confirm]."
msgstr ""
"{sles}{nbsp}15 构建主机需要 {sles} 模块 ``SLE-Module-DevTools15-SP2-Pool`` "
"和 ``SLE-Module-DevTools15-SP2-Updates``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:157
msgid ""
"Install Kiwi and all required packages by applying `Highstate`.  From the "
"system details page select menu:States[Highstate] and click btn:[Apply "
"Highstate].  Alternatively, apply Highstate from the {productname} Server "
"command line:"
msgstr ""
"通过应用 ``Highstate`` 安装 Kiwi 和所有必需的软件包。在系统细节页面中选择"
"menu:状态[Highstate]，然后单击 btn:[应用 Highstate]。或者，从 {productname} "
"Server 命令行应用 Highstate："

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:159
#, no-wrap
msgid "{productname} Web Server Public Certificate RPM"
msgstr "{productname} Web 服务器公共证书 RPM"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:160
msgid ""
"Build host provisioning copies the {productname} certificate RPM to the "
"build host.  This certificate is used for accessing repositories provided by "
"{productname}."
msgstr ""
"构建主机置备将 {productname} 证书 RPM 复制到构建主机。此证书用于访问 "
"{productname} 提供的储存库。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:161
msgid ""
"The certificate is packaged in RPM by the `mgr-package-rpm-certificate-"
"osimage` package script.  The package script is called automatically during "
"a new {productname} installation."
msgstr ""
"该证书由 `mgr-package-rpm-certificate-osimage` 打包脚本打包在 RPM 中。在全新"
"安装 {productname} 期间会自动调用该打包脚本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:162
msgid ""
"When you upgrade the `spacewalk-certs-tools` package, the upgrade scenario "
"calls the package script using the default values.  However if the "
"certificate path was changed or unavailable, call the package script "
"manually using `--ca-cert-full-path <path_to_certificate>` after the upgrade "
"procedure has finished."
msgstr ""
"当您升级 `spacewalk-certs-tools` 软件包时，升级方案会使用默认值调用该打包脚"
"本。但是，如果证书路径已更改或不可用，请在升级过程完成后使用 `--ca-cert-full-"
"path <证书路径>` 手动调用该打包脚本。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:163
#, no-wrap
msgid "Package script call example"
msgstr "打包脚本调用示例"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:164
#, no-wrap
msgid "/usr/sbin/mgr-package-rpm-certificate-osimage --ca-cert-full-path /root/ssl-build/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT\n"
msgstr "/usr/sbin/mgr-package-rpm-certificate-osimage --ca-cert-full-path /root/ssl-build/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:165
msgid ""
"The RPM package with the certificate is stored in a salt-accessible "
"directory such as:"
msgstr "包含证书的 RPM 软件包储存在 Salt 可访问的目录中，例如："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "/usr/share/susemanager/salt/images/rhn-org-trusted-ssl-cert-osimage-1.0-1.noarch.rpm\n"
msgstr "/usr/share/susemanager/salt/images/rhn-org-trusted-ssl-cert-osimage-1.0-1.noarch.rpm\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:167
msgid ""
"The RPM package with the certificate is provided in the local build host "
"repository:"
msgstr "包含证书的 RPM 软件包在本地构建主机储存库中提供："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:168
#, no-wrap
msgid "/var/lib/Kiwi/repo\n"
msgstr "/var/lib/Kiwi/repo\n"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:169
msgid ""
"Specify the RPM package with the {productname} SSL certificate in the build "
"source, and make sure your Kiwi configuration contains ``rhn-org-trusted-ssl-"
"cert-osimage`` as a required package in the ``bootstrap`` section."
msgstr ""
"在构建源中指定包含 {productname} SSL 证书的 RPM 软件包，并确保您的 Kiwi 配置"
"包含 ``rhn-org-trusted-ssl-cert-osimage`` 作为 ``bootstrap`` 部分中必需的软件"
"包。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:170
#, no-wrap
msgid "config.xml"
msgstr "config.xml"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:171
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"...\n"
"  <packages type=\"bootstrap\">\n"
"    ...\n"
"    <package name=\"rhn-org-trusted-ssl-cert-osimage\" bootinclude=\"true\"/>\n"
"  </packages>\n"
"...\n"
msgstr ""
"...\n"
"  <packages type=\"bootstrap\">\n"
"    ...\n"
"    <package name=\"rhn-org-trusted-ssl-cert-osimage\" bootinclude=\"true\"/>\n"
"  </packages>\n"
"...\n"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:172
#, no-wrap
msgid "Create an Activation Key for OS Images"
msgstr "为操作系统映像创建激活密钥"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:173
msgid ""
"Create an activation key associated with the channel that your OS Images can "
"use as repositories when building the image."
msgstr "创建与通道（在构建映像时操作系统映像可将其用作储存库）关联的激活密钥。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:174
msgid "Activation keys are mandatory for OS Image building."
msgstr "必须提供激活密钥才能构建操作系统映像。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:175
msgid ""
"To build OS Images, you need an activation key that is associated with a "
"channel other than `SUSE Manager Default`."
msgstr ""
"要构建操作系统映像，需要一个与通道关联的激活密钥，但该通道不能是 ``SUSE "
"Manager Default``。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:177
msgid "In the {webui}, select menu:Systems[Activation Keys]."
msgstr "在 {webui} 中，选择menu:系统[激活密钥]。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:178
msgid "Click [guimenu]``Create Key``."
msgstr "单击[guimenu]``创建密钥``。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:179
msgid ""
"Enter a [guimenu]``Description``, a [guimenu]``Key`` name, and use the drop-"
"down box to select a [guimenu]``Base Channel`` to associate with the key."
msgstr ""
"输入[guimenu]``说明``和[guimenu]``密钥名称``，并使用下拉框选择要与该密钥关联"
"的[guimenu]``基础通道``。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:183
msgid ""
"OS Images can require a significant amount of storage space.  Therefore, we "
"recommended that the OS Image store is located on a partition of its own or "
"on a Btrfs subvolume, separate from the root partition.  By default, the "
"image store is located at [path]``/srv/www/os-images``."
msgstr ""
"操作系统映像可能需要大量储存空间。因此，我们建议将操作系统映像储存放在其自身"
"所在的分区上或 Btrfs 子卷上，并与根分区分开。默认情况下，映像储存位于 "
"[path]``/srv/www/os-images``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:184
msgid ""
"Image stores for Kiwi build type, used to build system, virtual, and other "
"images, are not supported yet."
msgstr ""
"目前不支持 Kiwi 构建类型的用于构建系统映像、虚拟映像和其他映像的映像储存。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:185
msgid ""
"Images are always stored in [path]``/srv/www/os-images/<organization id>`` "
"and are accessible via HTTP/HTTPS [url]``https://<susemanager_host>/os-"
"images/<organization id>``."
msgstr ""
"映像始终储存在 [path]``/srv/www/os-images/<组织 ID>`` 中，可通过 HTTP/HTTPS "
"[url]``https://<SUSE Manager 主机>/os-images/<组织 ID>`` 访问。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:187
msgid "Manage image profiles using the {webui}."
msgstr "使用 {webui} 管理映像配置文件。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:190
msgid ""
"To create an image profile select from menu:Images[Profiles] and click btn:"
"[Create]."
msgstr ""
"要创建映像配置文件，请在menu:映像[配置文件]中选择，然后单击 btn:[创建]。"

#. type: Target for macro image
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:191
#, no-wrap
msgid "images_image_create_profile_kiwi.png"
msgstr "images_image_create_profile_kiwi.png"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:192
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Label`` field, provide a name for the `Image Profile`."
msgstr "在[guimenu]``标签``字段中，提供``映像配置文件``的名称。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:193
msgid "Use `Kiwi` as the [guimenu]``Image Type``."
msgstr "使用 `Kiwi` 作为[guimenu]``映像类型``。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:194
msgid "Image store is automatically selected."
msgstr "系统会自动选择映像储存。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:195
msgid ""
"Enter a [guimenu]``Config URL`` to the directory containing the Kiwi "
"configuration files:"
msgstr "输入指向包含 Kiwi 配置文件的目录的[guimenu]``配置 URL``："

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:196
msgid "git URI"
msgstr "git URI"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:197
msgid "HTTPS tarball"
msgstr "HTTPS tarball"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:198
msgid "Path to build host local directory"
msgstr "构建主机本地目录的路径"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:199
msgid ""
"Enter [guimenu]``Kiwi options`` if needed.  If the Kiwi configuration files "
"specify multiple profiles, use [option]``--profile <name>`` to select the "
"active one."
msgstr ""
"根据需要输入 [guimenu]``Kiwi 选项``。如果 Kiwi 配置文件指定了多个配置文件，请"
"使用 [option]``--profile <名称>`` 选择活动配置文件。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:200
msgid "For other options, see Kiwi documentation."
msgstr "有关其他选项，请参见 Kiwi 文档。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:201
msgid ""
"Select an [guimenu]``Activation Key``.  Activation keys ensure that images "
"using a profile are assigned to the correct channel and packages."
msgstr ""
"选择一个[guimenu]``激活密钥``。激活密钥可确保将使用配置文件的映像指派到正确的"
"通道和软件包。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:202
msgid ""
"Associate an activation key with an image profile to ensure the image "
"profile uses the correct software channel, and any packages."
msgstr ""
"将激活密钥与映像配置文件相关联，以确保映像配置文件使用正确的软件通道和任何软"
"件包。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:203
msgid "Confirm with the btn:[Create] button."
msgstr "选择 btn:[创建] 按钮以确认。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:204
#, no-wrap
msgid "Source format options"
msgstr "源格式选项"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:205
msgid "git/HTTP(S) URL to the repository"
msgstr "指向储存库的 git/HTTP(S) URL"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:206
msgid ""
"URL to the git repository containing the sources of the image to be built.  "
"Depending on the layout of the repository the URL can be:"
msgstr ""
"指向要构建的映像的源所在 git 储存库的 URL。根据储存库的布局，该 URL 可能是："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:207
#, no-wrap
