msgstr "https://github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:208
msgid ""
"You can specify a branch after the `#` character in the URL.  In this "
"example, we use the `master` branch:"
msgstr "可以在 URL 中的 `#` 字符后面指定一个分支。此示例使用了 `master` 分支："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:209
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles#master\n"
msgstr "https://github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles#master\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:210
msgid ""
"You can specify a directory that contains the image sources after the `:` "
"character.  In this example, we use `OSImage/POS_Image-JeOS6`:"
msgstr ""
"可以在 `:` 字符后面指定包含映像源的目录。此示例使用了 `OSImage/POS_Image-"
"JeOS6`："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:211
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles#master:OSImage/POS_Image-JeOS6\n"
msgstr "https://github.com/SUSE/manager-build-profiles#master:OSImage/POS_Image-JeOS6\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:212
msgid "HTTP(S) URL to the tarball"
msgstr "指向 tarball 的 HTTP(S) URL"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:213
msgid ""
"URL to the tar archive, compressed or uncompressed, hosted on the webserver."
msgstr "指向托管在 Web 服务器上的 tar 存档（压缩或未压缩）的 URL。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:214
#, no-wrap
msgid "https://myimagesourceserver.example.org/MyKiwiImage.tar.gz\n"
msgstr "https://myimagesourceserver.example.org/MyKiwiImage.tar.gz\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:215
msgid "Path to the directory on the build host"
msgstr "构建主机上的目录的路径"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/image-management.adoc:216
msgid ""
"Enter the path to the directory with the Kiwi build system sources.  This "
