#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:19
msgid ""
"{productname} releases maintenance updates (MUs) to provide newer packages.  "
"Maintenance updates are indicated with a new version number.  For example, "
"the major release 4.1 is incremented to 4.1.1 when an MU is released."
msgstr ""
"{productname} 会发布维护更新 (MU) 以提供较新的软件包。维护更新用新的版本号表"
"示。例如，在发布 MU 后，主发行版 4.1 将递增为 4.1.1。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:20
msgid ""
"You can verify which version you are running by looking at the bottom of the "
"navigation bar in the {webui}.  You can also fetch the version number with "
"the [literal]``api.getVersion()`` XMLRPC API call."
msgstr ""
"可以通过查看 {webui} 中导航栏底部的信息来校验您正在运行的版本。还可以使用 "
"[literal]``api.getVersion()`` XMLRPC API 调用来获取版本号。"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Client Tools"
msgstr "客户端工具"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:22
msgid ""
"When the server is updated consider updating some tools on the clients, "
"too.  Updating [package]``salt-minion``, [package]``zypper``, and other "
"related management package on clients is not a strict requirement, but it is "
"a best practice in general.  For example, a maintenance update on the server "
"might introduce a major new Salt version.  Then Salt clients continue to "
"work but might experience problems later on.  To avoid this always update "
"the [package]``salt-minion`` package when available.  {suse} makes sure that "
"[package]``salt-minion`` can always be updated safely."
msgstr ""
"当服务器更新时，请考虑同时更新客户端上的某些工具。并非一定要更新客户端上的 "
"[package]``salt-minion``、[package]``zypper`` 和其他相关管理软件包，但一般情"
"况下最好这样做。例如，服务器上的维护更新可能会引入新的 Salt 主版本。然后，"
"Salt 客户端有一段时间可以继续正常运行，但后来可能会出现问题。为了避免这种情"
"况，在适当的情况下请务必更新 [package]``salt-minion`` 软件包。{suse} 确保始终"
"可以安全更新 [package]``salt-minion``。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Inter-Server Synchronization Slave Server"
msgstr "服务器间同步从属服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:24
msgid ""
"If you are using an inter-server synchronization slave server, update it "
"after the {productname} Server update is complete."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用服务器间同步从属服务器，请在 {productname} Server 更新完成后对其进"
"行更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:25
msgid ""
"For more in inter-server synchronization, see xref:administration:iss.adoc[]."
msgstr "有关服务器间同步的详细信息，请参见 xref:administration:iss.adoc[]。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Monitoring Server"
msgstr "监视服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:27
msgid ""
"If you are using a monitoring server for Prometheus, update it after the "
"{productname} Server update is complete."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用 Prometheus 监视服务器，请在 {productname} Server 更新完成后对其进"
"行更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:28
msgid ""
"For more information on monitoring, see xref:administration:monitoring."
"adoc[]."
msgstr "有关监视的详细信息，请参见 xref:administration:monitoring.adoc[]。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Proxy"
msgstr "代理"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:30
msgid ""
"Proxies should be updated as soon as {productname} Server updates are "
"complete."
msgstr "{productname} Server 更新完成后，代理应会立即更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:31
msgid ""
"In general, running a proxy connected to a server on a different version is "
"not supported.  The only exception is for the duration of updates where it "
"is expected that the server is updated first, so the proxy could run the "
"previous version temporarily."
msgstr ""
"一般情况下，不支持运行与其他版本上的服务器相连接的代理。唯一的例外情况是在更"
"新期间，预期首先会更新服务器，因此代理可能暂时运行旧版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:32
msgid ""
"Especially if you are migrating from version 4.0 to 4.1, upgrade the server "
"first, then any proxy."
msgstr ""
"尤其是从版本 4.0 迁移到版本 4.1 时，请先升级服务器，然后再升级任何代理。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/infra-maintenance.adoc:33
msgid ""
"For more information, see xref:installation-and-upgrade:proxy-intro.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息，请参见 xref:installation-and-upgrade:proxy-intro.adoc[]。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Inter-Server Synchronization"
msgstr "服务器间同步"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you have more than one {productname} installation, you need to ensure "
"that they stay aligned on content and permissions.  Inter-Server "
"Synchronization (ISS) allows you to connect two or more {productname} "
"Servers and keep them up-to-date."
msgstr ""
"如果您安装了多个 {productname}，需要确保它们在内容和权限方面保持一致。服务器"
"间同步 (ISS) 允许连接两个或更多个 {productname} Server 并使它们保持最新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:3
msgid ""
"To set up ISS, you need to define one {productname} Server as a master, with "
"the other as a slave.  If conflicting configurations exist, the system "
"prioritizes the master configuration."
msgstr ""
"要设置 ISS，需要将一个 {productname} Server 定义为主服务器，将另一个定义为从"
"属服务器。如果配置有冲突，系统会优先使用主服务器配置。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:4
msgid ""
"ISS Masters are masters only because they have slaves attached to them.  "
"This means that you need to set up the ISS Master first, by defining its "
"slaves.  You can then set up the ISS Slaves, by attaching them to a master."
msgstr ""
"ISS 主服务器之所以称为主服务器，只因为其上挂接了从属服务器。这意味着，需要首"
"先通过定义其从属服务器来设置 ISS 主服务器。然后通过将 ISS 从属服务器挂接到主"
"服务器来设置从属服务器。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Setting up an ISS Master"
msgstr "过程：设置 ISS 主服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:6
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Admin[ISS Configuration > "
"Master Setup], and click btn:[Add new slave]."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，导航到menu:管理[ISS 配置 > 主服务器设置]，然后单"
"击 btn:[添加新的从属服务器]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:7
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Edit Slave Details`` dialog, provide these details for the "
"ISS Master's first slave:"
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``编辑从属服务器细节``对话框中，为 ISS 主服务器的第一个从属服务器"
"提供以下细节："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:8
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Slave Fully Qualified Domain Name`` field, enter the FQDN "
"of the ISS Slave."
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``从属服务器的完全限定域名``字段中，输入 ISS 从属服务器的 FQDN。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:9
msgid "For example: [systemitem]``server2.example.com``."
msgstr "例如：[systemitem]``server2.example.com``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Allow Slave to Sync?`` checkbox to enable the slave to "
"synchronize with the master."
msgstr ""
"选中[guimenu]``允许从属服务器同步？``复选框以启用从属服务器与主服务器的同步。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Sync All Orgs to Slave?`` checkbox to synchronize all "
"organizations to this slave."
msgstr ""
"选中[guimenu]``将所有组织同步到从属服务器？``复选框以将所有组织同步到此从属服"
"务器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:12
msgid "Click btn:[Create] to add the ISS slave."
msgstr "单击 btn:[创建] 以添加 ISS 从属服务器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:13
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Allow Export of the Selected Organizations`` section, "
"check the organizations you want to allow this slave to export to the "
"master, and click btn:[Allow Orgs]."
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``允许导出所选组织``部分，选中您要允许在其中将此从属服务器导出到主"
"服务器的组织，然后单击 btn:[允许组织]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Before you set up the ISS Slave, you need to ensure you have the appropriate "
"CA certificate."
msgstr "在设置 ISS 从属服务器之前，需要确保拥有适当的 CA 证书。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Copying the Master CA Certificate to an ISS Slave"
msgstr "过程：将主服务器 CA 证书复制到 ISS 从属服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:16
msgid ""
"On the ISS Master, locate the CA Certificate at ``/srv/www/htdocs/pub/RHN-"
"ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT`` and create a copy that can be transferred to the "
"ISS Slave."
msgstr ""
"在 ISS 主服务器上的 ``/srv/www/htdocs/pub/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT`` 中找到 "
"CA 证书，并创建一个可传输到 ISS 从属服务器的副本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:17
msgid ""
"On the ISS Slave, save the CA certificate file to the ``/etc/pki/trust/"
"anchors/`` directory."
msgstr ""
"在 ISS 从属服务器上，将 CA 证书文件保存到 ``/etc/pki/trust/anchors/`` 目录。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:18
msgid "When you have copied the certificate, you can set up the ISS Slave."
msgstr "复制证书后，可以设置 ISS 从属服务器。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Setting up an ISS Slave"
msgstr "过程：设置 ISS 从属服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:20
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Admin[ISS Configuration > "
"Slave Setup], and click btn:[Add new master]."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，导航到menu:管理[ISS 配置 > 从属服务器设置]，然后"
"单击 btn:[添加新的主服务器]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:21
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Details for new Master`` dialog, provide these details for "
"the server to use as the ISS master:"
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``新主服务器细节``对话框中，为用作 ISS 主服务器的服务器提供以下细"
"节："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:22
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Master Fully Qualified Domain Name`` field, enter the FQDN "
"of the ISS Master for this slave."
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``主服务器的完全限定域名``字段中，输入此从属服务器的 ISS 主服务器"
"的 FQDN。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:23
msgid "For example: ``server1.example.com``."
msgstr "例如：``server1.example.com``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:24
msgid ""
"In the [guimenu]``Filename of this Master's CA Certificate`` field, enter "
"the absolute path to the CA certificate on the ISS master."
msgstr ""
"在[guimenu]``此主服务器 CA 证书的文件名``字段中，输入 CA 证书在 ISS 主服务器"
"上的绝对路径。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:25
msgid "This should be ``/etc/pki/trust/anchors/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT``."
msgstr "此路径应是 ``/etc/pki/trust/anchors/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:26
msgid "Click btn:[Add new master] to add the ISS Slave to this master."
msgstr "单击 btn:[添加新的主服务器] 将 ISS 从属服务器添加到此主服务器。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Completing ISS Setup"
msgstr "过程：完成 ISS 设置"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:28
msgid ""
"At the command prompt on the ISS Slave, synchronize with the ISS Master:"
msgstr "在 ISS 从属服务器上的命令提示符下，与 ISS 主服务器同步："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-inter-sync\n"
msgstr "mgr-inter-sync\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:30
msgid "OPTIONAL: To synchronize a single channel, use this command:"
msgstr "可选：要同步单个通道，请使用以下命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-inter-sync -c <channel-name>\n"
msgstr "mgr-inter-sync -c <通道名称>\n"

#.  Need to double check this against the UI. --LKB 2020-04-08
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss.adoc:32
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Admin[ISS Configuration > "
"Configure Master-to-Slave Mappings] and select the organizations you want to "
"synchronize."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，导航到menu:管理[ISS 配置 > 配置主-从属服务器映"
"射]，并选择要同步的组织。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Inter-Server Synchronization - Version 2"
msgstr "服务器间同步 - 版本 2"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you have more than one {productname} installation, you will need to copy "
"contents between servers.  Inter-Server Synchronization (ISS) allows you to "
"export data from one server (source) and import it on another (target) "
"server.  This is useful for hub deployment scenarios or disconnected setups."
msgstr ""
"如果您安装了多个 {productname}，有时需要在服务器之间复制内容。使用服务器间同"
"步 (ISS) 可以导出一台服务器（源）的数据，并将其导入另一台（目标）服务器。这对"
"于中心部署方案或断开连接的设置很有用。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:3
msgid ""
"With the version 2 ISS implementation {SUSE} removed the master/slave "
"notion.  Contents can be exported and imported in any direction between any "
"{productname} server."
msgstr ""
"在第 2 版 ISS 实现中，{SUSE} 去除了主/从概念。可以在任何 {productname} 服务器"
"之间朝任一方向导出和导入内容。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "Install ISS Packages"
msgstr "安装 ISS 软件包"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:5
msgid ""
"To use ISS you need to install the [package]``inter-server-sync`` package on "
"source and target servers."
msgstr ""
"要使用 ISS，需要在源服务器和目标服务器上安装 [package]``inter-server-sync`` "
"软件包。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Content Synchronization"
msgstr "内容同步"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Export data on source server"
msgstr "过程：导出源服务器上的数据"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:8
msgid ""
"On the source server, on the command line execute the ISS export command.  "
"The [option]``-h`` option provides detailed help:"
msgstr ""
"在源服务器上的命令行中执行 ISS export 命令。[option]``-h`` 选项可提供详细帮"
"助："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "inter-server-sync export -h\n"
msgstr "inter-server-sync export -h\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:10
msgid ""
"The export procedure creates an output directory with all the needed data "
"for the import procedure."
msgstr "导出过程会创建一个输出目录，其中包含导入过程所需的所有数据。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Copy export directory to target server"
msgstr "过程：将导出目录复制到目标服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Contents from the source server needs to be synchronized to the target "
"server.  On the command line, as root, execute:"
msgstr ""
"需要将源服务器中的内容同步到目标服务器。在命令行中，以 root 身份执行以下命"
"令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "rsync -r <PATH_EXPORTED_DIR> root@<TARGET_SERVER>:~/\n"
msgstr "rsync -r <导出目录的路径> root@<目标服务器>:~/\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:14
msgid "When all contents is copied, start importing it."
msgstr "复制所有内容后，开始导入这些内容。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Import data on target server"
msgstr "过程：在目标服务器上导入数据"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:16
msgid ""
"On the target server, on the command line execute the ISS import command.  "
"The [option]``-h`` option provides detailed help:"
msgstr ""
"在目标服务器上的命令行中执行 ISS import 命令。[option]``-h`` 选项可提供详细帮"
"助："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "inter-server-sync import -h\n"
msgstr "inter-server-sync import -h\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Database connection configuration"
msgstr "数据库连接配置"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/iss_v2.adoc:19
msgid ""
"Database connection configuration is loaded by default from ``/etc/rhn/rhn."
"conf``.  Properties file location can be overridden with parameter ``--"
"serverConfig``."
msgstr ""
