#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using ``mgr-sync``"
msgstr "使用 ``mgr-sync``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:2
msgid ""
"The ``mgr-sync`` tool is used at the command prompt.  It provides functions "
"for using {productname} that are not always available in the {webui}.  The "
"primary use of ``mgr-sync`` is to connect to the {scc}, retrieve product and "
"package information, and prepare channels for synchronization with the "
"{productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"需要在命令提示符下使用 ``mgr-sync`` 工具。此工具提供用于操作 {productname} 的"
"功能，而 {webui} 不一定提供这些功能。``mgr-sync`` 的主要用途是连接到 {scc}，"
"检索产品和软件包信息，并准备好要与 {productname} Server 同步的通道。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:3
msgid ""
"This tool is designed for use with a {suse} support subscription.  It is not "
"required for open source distributions, including {opensuse}, {centos}, and "
"{ubuntu}."
msgstr ""
"此工具应与 {suse} 支持订阅配合使用。{opensuse}、{centos} 和 {ubuntu} 等开源发"
"行套件不需要此工具。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:4
msgid ""
"The available commands and arguments for ``mgr-sync`` are listed in this "
"table.  Use this syntax for ``mgr-sync`` commands:"
msgstr ""
"下表中列出了 ``mgr-sync`` 的可用命令和参数。请对 ``mgr-sync`` 命令使用以下语"
"法："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-sync [-h] [--version] [-v] [-s] [-d {1,2,3}] {list,add,refresh,delete}\n"
msgstr "mgr-sync [-h] [--version] [-v] [-s] [-d {1,2,3}] {list,add,refresh,delete}\n"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-sync Commands"
msgstr "mgr-sync 命令"

#. type: Table
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Command | Description | Example Use\n"
"| list | List channels, organization credentials, or products | ``mgr-sync list channels``\n"
"| add | Add channels, organization credentials, or products | ``mgr-sync add channel <channel_name>``\n"
"| refresh | Refresh the local copy of products, channels, and subscriptions | ``mgr-sync refresh``\n"
"| delete | Delete existing SCC organization credentials from the local system | ``mgr-sync delete credentials``\n"
"| sync | Synchronize specified channel or ask for it when left blank| ``mgr-sync sync channel <channel_name>``\n"
msgstr ""
"| 命令 | 说明 | 示例用法\n"
"| list | 列出通道、组织身份凭证或产品 | ``mgr-sync list channels``\n"
"| add | 添加通道、组织身份凭证或产品 | ``mgr-sync add channel <通道名称>``\n"
"| refresh | 刷新产品、通道和订阅的本地副本 | ``mgr-sync refresh``\n"
"| delete | 从本地系统中删除现有的 SCC 组织身份凭证 | ``mgr-sync delete credentials``\n"
"| sync | 同步指定的通道，如果将通道名称留空，则请求提供名称| ``mgr-sync sync channel <通道名称>``\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:8
msgid ""
"To see the full list of options specific to a command, use this command:"
msgstr "要查看特定于某个命令的完整选项列表，请使用以下命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-sync <command> --help\n"
msgstr "mgr-sync <命令> --help\n"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-sync Optional Arguments"
msgstr "mgr-sync 可选参数"

#. type: Table
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Option | Abbreviated option | Description | Example Use\n"
"| help | ``h`` | Display the command usage and options | ``mgr-sync --help``\n"
"| version | N/A | Display the currently installed version of ``mgr-sync`` | ``mgr-sync --version``\n"
"| verbose | ``v`` | Provide verbose output | ``mgr-sync --verbose refresh``\n"
"| store-credentials | ``s`` | Store credentials a local hidden file | ``mgr-sync --store-credentials``\n"
"| debug | ``d`` | Log additional debugging information. Requires a level of 1, 2, 3. 3 provides the highest amnount of debugging information | ``mgr-sync -d 3 refresh``\n"
"| no-sync | N/A | Use with the ``add`` command to add products or channels without beginning a synchronization | ``mgr-sync --no-sync add <channel_name>``\n"
msgstr ""
"| 选项 | 选项缩写 | 说明 | 示例用法\n"
"| help | ``h`` | 显示命令用法和选项 | ``mgr-sync --help``\n"
"| version | 不适用 | 显示当前安装的 ``mgr-sync`` 版本 | ``mgr-sync --version``\n"
"| verbose | ``v`` | 提供详细输出 | ``mgr-sync --verbose refresh``\n"
"| store-credentials | ``s`` | 将身份凭证储存在本地隐藏文件中 | ``mgr-sync --store-credentials``\n"
"| debug | ``d`` | 记录附加调试信息。需要指定级别 1、2、3。3 提供的调试信息量最多 | ``mgr-sync -d 3 refresh``\n"
"| no-sync | 不适用 | 与 ``add`` 命令结合使用，以添加产品或通道，而无需开始同步 | ``mgr-sync --no-sync add <通道名称>``\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:12
msgid "Logs for ``mgr-sync`` are located in:"
msgstr "``mgr-sync`` 的日志位于："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:13
msgid "[path]``/var/log/rhn/mgr-sync.log``"
msgstr "[path]``/var/log/rhn/mgr-sync.log``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mgr-sync.adoc:14
msgid "[path]``/var/log/rhn/rhn_web_api.log``"
msgstr "[path]``/var/log/rhn/rhn_web_api.log``"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mirror Source Packages"
msgstr "镜像源软件包"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you build your own packages locally, or if you require the source code "
"for your packages for legal reasons, it is possible to mirror the source "
"packages on {productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"如果您在本地构建自己的软件包，或者出于法律原因需要提供软件包的源代码，可以在 "
"{productname} Server 上镜像源软件包。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:3
msgid ""
"Mirroring source packages can consume a significant amount of disk space."
msgstr "镜像源软件包可能会消耗大量磁盘空间。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Mirroring Source Packages"
msgstr "过程：镜像源软件包"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:5
msgid ""
"Open the [filename]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` configuration file, and add this "
"line:"
msgstr "打开 [filename]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` 配置文件并添加下面一行内容："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "server.sync_source_packages = 1\n"
msgstr "server.sync_source_packages = 1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:7
msgid "Restart the Spacewalk service to pick up the changes:"
msgstr "重启动 Spacewalk 服务以应用更改："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Currently, this feature can only be enabled globally for all repositories.  "
"It is not possible to select individual repositories for mirroring."
msgstr "目前，只能为所有储存库全局启用此功能。无法选择单个要镜像的储存库。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/mirror-sources.adoc:10
msgid ""
"When this feature has been activated, the source packages become available "
"in the {productname} {webui} after the next repository synchronization.  "
"They are shown as sources for the binary package, and can be downloaded "
"directly from the {webui}.  Source packages cannot be installed on clients "
"using the {webui}."
msgstr ""
"激活此功能后，源软件包会在下次储存库同步后显示在 {productname} {webui} 中。它"
"们显示为二进制软件包的源，可以直接从 {webui} 下载。无法使用 {webui} 在客户端"
"上安装源软件包。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Monitoring with Prometheus and Grafana"
msgstr "使用 Prometheus 和 Grafana 进行监视"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:2
msgid ""
"You can monitor your {productname} environment using Prometheus and "
"Grafana.  {productname} Server and Proxy are able to provide self-health "
"metrics.  You can also install and manage a number of Prometheus exporters "
"on Salt clients."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 Prometheus 和 Grafana 监视 {productname} 环境。{productname} "
"Server 和 Proxy 能够提供自我运行状况监视度量。您还可以在 Salt 客户端上安装和"
"管理一些 Prometheus 导出器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:3
msgid ""
"Prometheus and Grafana packages are included in the {productname} Client "
"Tools for:"
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 和 Grafana 软件包包含在以下发行套件的 {productname} 客户端工具中："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:4
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:7
msgid "{sle}{nbsp}12"
msgstr "{sle}{nbsp}12"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:5
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:8
msgid "{sle}{nbsp}15"
msgstr "{sle}{nbsp}15"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:6
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:9
msgid "openSUSE Leap 15.x"
msgstr "openSUSE Leap 15.x"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:10
msgid ""
"You need to install Prometheus and Grafana on a machine separate from the "
"{productname} Server.  We recommend to use a managed Salt {suse} client as "
"your monitoring server.  Other clients are not supported as a monitoring "
"server."
msgstr ""
"需要在不包含 {productname} Server 的计算机上安装 Prometheus 和 Grafana。我们"
"建议使用受管 Salt {suse} 客户端作为监视服务器。不支持使用其他客户端作为监视服"
"务器。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Prometheus fetches metrics using a pull mechanism, so the server must be "
"able to establish TCP connections to monitored clients.  Clients must have "
"corresponding open ports and be reachable over the network.  Alternatively, "
"you can use reverse proxies to establish a connection."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 使用拉取机制提取度量，因此服务器必须能够与受监视客户端建立 TCP 连"
"接。客户端上必须打开相应的端口，并且必须可以通过网络访问客户端。或者，您可以"
"使用反向代理来建立连接。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:12
msgid ""
"You must have a monitoring add-on subscription for each client you want to "
"monitor.  Visit the {scc} to manage your {productname} subscriptions."
msgstr ""
"对于您要监视的每个客户端，必须有一个监视附加订阅。访问 {scc} 以管理您的 "
"{productname} 订阅。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Prometheus and Grafana"
msgstr "Prometheus 和 Grafana"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Prometheus"
msgstr "Prometheus"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:15
msgid ""
"Prometheus is an open-source monitoring tool that is used to record real-"
"time metrics in a time-series database.  Metrics are pulled via HTTP, "
"enabling high performance and scalability."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 是一个开源监视工具，用于在时序数据库中记录实时度量。度量通过 HTTP "
"拉取，从而可以实现高性能和可伸缩性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:16
msgid ""
"Prometheus metrics are time series data, or timestamped values belonging to "
"the same group or dimension.  A metric is uniquely identified by its name "
"and set of labels."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 度量是时序数据，或者是属于同一个组或维度的带时间戳值。度量由其名称"
"和一组标签唯一标识。"

#.  TODO:: This should be an actual image.
#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   metric name               labels                 timestamp     value\n"
"┌────────┴───────┐  ┌───────────┴───────────┐    ┌──────┴──────┐  ┌─┴─┐\n"
"http_requests_total{status=\"200\", method=\"GET\"}  @1557331801.111  42236\n"
msgstr ""
"   度量名称               标签                 时间戳     值\n"
"┌────────┴───────┐  ┌───────────┴───────────┐    ┌──────┴──────┐  ┌─┴─┐\n"
"http_requests_total{status=\"200\", method=\"GET\"}  @1557331801.111  42236\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Each application or system being monitored must expose metrics in the format "
"above, either through code instrumentation or Prometheus exporters."
msgstr ""
"每个受监视的应用程序或系统必须通过代码检测或 Prometheus 导出器按上述格式公开"
"度量。"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Prometheus Exporters"
msgstr "Prometheus 导出器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:20
msgid ""
"Exporters are libraries that help with exporting metrics from third-party "
"systems as Prometheus metrics.  Exporters are useful whenever it is not "
"feasible to instrument a given application or system with Prometheus metrics "
"directly.  Multiple exporters can run on a monitored host to export local "
"metrics."
msgstr ""
"导出器是帮助将第三方系统中的度量作为 Prometheus 度量导出的库。每当无法直接使"
"用 Prometheus 度量检测给定的应用程序或系统时，导出器就很有作用。可以在受监视"
"主机上运行多个导出器以导出本地度量。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:21
msgid ""
"The Prometheus community provides a list of official exporters, and more can "
"be found as community contributions.  For more information and an extensive "
"list of exporters, see https://prometheus.io/docs/instrumenting/exporters/."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 社区提供了官方导出器的列表，还有其他一些作为社区贡献内容提供的导出"
"器。有关详细信息和导出器的详细列表，请参见 link:https://prometheus.io/docs/"
"instrumenting/exporters/[]。"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Grafana"
msgstr "Grafana"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:23
msgid ""
"Grafana is a tool for data visualization, monitoring, and analysis.  It is "
"used to create dashboards with panels representing specific metrics over a "
"set period of time.  Grafana is commonly used together with Prometheus, but "
"also supports other data sources such as ElasticSearch, MySQL, PostgreSQL, "
"and Influx DB.  For more information about Grafana, see https://grafana.com/"
"docs/."
msgstr ""
"Grafana 是一个数据可视化、监视和分析工具。它用于创建仪表板，其中的面板代表设"
"置时间段内的特定度量。Grafana 通常与 Prometheus 一起使用，但也支持 "
"ElasticSearch、MySQL、PostgreSQL 和 Influx DB 等其他数据源。有关 Grafana 的详"
"细信息，请参见 link:https://grafana.com/docs/[]。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Set up the Monitoring Server"
msgstr "设置监视服务器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:25
msgid ""
"To set up your monitoring server, you need to install Prometheus and "
"Grafana, and configure them."
msgstr "要设置监视服务器，需要安装 Prometheus 和 Grafana 并对其进行配置。"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Install Prometheus"
msgstr "安装 Prometheus"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:27
msgid ""
"If your monitoring server is a Salt client, you can install the Prometheus "
"package using the {productname} {webui}.  Otherwise you can download and "
"install the package on your monitoring server manually.  The Prometheus "
"software is also available for {productname} Proxy and {productname} {smr} "
"Branch Server."
msgstr ""
"如果您的监视服务器是 Salt 客户端，则您可以使用 {productname} {webui} 安装 "
"Prometheus 软件包。否则，可以在监视服务器上手动下载并安装该软件包。"
"Prometheus 软件也可用于 {productname} Proxy 和 {productname} {smr} Branch "
"Server。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Prometheus expects POSIX filesystem for storing data.  Non-POSIX compliant "
"filesystems are not supported.  NFS filesystems are not supported."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 需要使用 POSIX 文件系统来储存数据。不支持不符合 POSIX 标准的文件系"
"统，因此不支持 NFS 文件系统。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Installing Prometheus Using the {webui}"
msgstr "过程：使用 {webui} 安装 Prometheus"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:30
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, open the details page of the system where "
"Prometheus is to be installed, and navigate to the [guimenu]``Formulas`` tab."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，打开要在其中安装 Prometheus 的系统的细节页面，然"
"后导航到[guimenu]``配置模板集``选项卡。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:31
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Prometheus`` checkbox to enable monitoring formulas, "
"and click btn:[Save]."
msgstr ""
"选中 [guimenu]``Prometheus`` 复选框以启用监视配置模板集，然后单击 btn:[保"
"存]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:32
msgid "Navigate to the ``Prometheus`` tab in the top menu."
msgstr "在顶部菜单中导航到 ``Prometheus`` 选项卡。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:33
msgid ""
"In the ``{productname} Server`` section, enter valid {productname} API "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"在 ``{productname} Server`` 部分，输入有效的 {productname} API 身份凭证。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:34
msgid ""
"Make sure that the credentials you have entered allow access to the set of "
"systems you want to monitor."
msgstr "确保您输入的身份凭证允许访问您要监视的系统集。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:35
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:64
msgid "Customize any other configuration options according to your needs."
msgstr "根据需要自定义任何其他配置选项。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:36
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:65
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:148
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:178
msgid "Click btn:[Save Formula]."
msgstr "单击 btn:[保存配置模板集]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:37
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:66
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:179
msgid "Apply the highstate and confirm that it completes successfully."
msgstr "应用 Highstate 并确认它成功完成。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:38
