"Check the [guimenu]``Enabled`` checkbox on the ``Prometheus Exporters`` "
"formula."
msgstr "选中 ``Prometheus 导出器``配置模板集对应的[guimenu]``已启用``复选框。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:145
