msgstr "grafana-cli --configOverrides cfg:default.paths.data=/var/lib/grafana --homepath /usr/share/grafana admin reset-admin-password <新口令>\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:158
#, no-wrap
msgid "Network Boundaries"
msgstr "网络边界"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:159
msgid ""
"Prometheus fetches metrics using a pull mechanism, so the server must be "
"able to establish TCP connections to monitored clients.  By default, "
"Prometheus uses these ports:"
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 使用拉取机制提取度量，因此服务器必须能够与受监视客户端建立 TCP 连"
"接。Prometheus 默认使用以下端口："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:160
msgid "Node exporter: 9100"
msgstr "Node 导出器：9100"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:161
msgid "PostgreSQL exporter: 9187"
msgstr "PostgreSQL 导出器：9187"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:162
msgid "Apache exporter: 9117"
msgstr "Apache 导出器：9117"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:163
msgid ""
"Additionally, if you are running the alert manager on a different host than "
"where you run Prometheus, you also need to open port 9093."
msgstr ""
"此外，如果您不是在运行 Prometheus 的同一台主机上运行警报管理器，则还需要在所"
"在主机上打开端口 9093。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:164
msgid ""
"For clients installed on cloud instances, you can add the required ports to "
"a security group that has access to the monitoring server."
msgstr ""
"对于安装在云实例上的客户端，可以将所需的端口添加到有权访问监视服务器的安全组"
"中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:165
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can deploy a Prometheus instance in the exporters' local "
"network, and configure federation.  This allows the main monitoring server "
"to scrape the time series from the local Prometheus instance.  If you use "
"this method, you only need to open the Prometheus API port, which is 9090."
msgstr ""
"或者，可以在导出器的本地网络中部署 Prometheus 实例，并配置联合。这样，主监视"
"服务器就能从本地 Prometheus 实例中抓取时序。如果您使用此方法，只需要打开 "
"Prometheus API 端口 (9090) 即可。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:166
msgid ""
"For more information on Prometheus federation, see https://prometheus.io/"
"docs/prometheus/latest/federation/."
msgstr ""
"有关 Prometheus 联合的详细信息，请参见 link:https://prometheus.io/docs/"
"prometheus/latest/federation/[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:167
msgid ""
"You can also proxy requests through the network boundary.  Tools like "
"PushProx deploy a proxy and a client on both sides of the network barrier "
"and allow Prometheus to work across network topologies such as NAT."
msgstr ""
"您还可以通过网络边界来中转请求。PushProx 等工具会在网络屏障的两端部署代理和客"
"户端，并允许 Prometheus 跨网络拓扑（例如 NAT）工作。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:168
msgid ""
"For more information on PushProx, see https://github.com/RobustPerception/"
"PushProx."
msgstr ""
"有关 PushProx 的详细信息，请参见 link:https://github.com/RobustPerception/"
"PushProx[]。"

#. type: Title ===
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:169
#, no-wrap
msgid "Reverse Proxy Setup"
msgstr "反向代理设置"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:170
msgid ""
"Prometheus fetches metrics using a pull mechanism, so the server must be "
"able to establish TCP connections to each exporter on the monitored "
"clients.  To simplify your firewall configuration, you can use reverse proxy "
"for your exporters to expose all metrics on a single port."
msgstr ""
"Prometheus 使用拉取机制提取度量，因此服务器必须能够与受监视客户端上的每个导出"
"器建立 TCP 连接。为了简化防火墙配置，可为导出器使用反向代理，以便在单个端口上"
"公开所有度量。"

#.  Probably a diagram here. --LKB 2020-08-11
#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:171
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Installing Prometheus Exporters with Reverse Proxy"
msgstr "过程：安装使用反向代理的 Prometheus 导出器"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:172
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, open the details page of the system to be "
"monitored, and navigate to the [guimenu]``Formulas`` tab."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，打开要监视的系统的细节页面，并导航到[guimenu]``"
"配置模板集``选项卡。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:173
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Prometheus Exporters`` checkbox to enable the exporters "
"formula, and click btn:[Save]."
msgstr ""
"选中 [guimenu]``Prometheus 导出器``复选框以启用导出器配置模板集，然后单击 "
"btn:[保存]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:174
msgid "Navigate to the ``Prometheus Exporters`` tab in the top menu."
msgstr "在顶部菜单中导航到 ``Prometheus 导出器``选项卡。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:175
msgid ""
"Check the [guimenu]``Enable reverse proxy`` option, and enter a valid "
"reverse proxy port number."
msgstr "选中[guimenu]``启用反向代理``选项，并输入有效的反向代理端口号。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:176
msgid "For example, ``9999``."
msgstr "例如 ``9999``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:177
msgid "Customize the other exporters according to your needs."
