"须由用户提供和部署。在 {productname} 中可以启用以下安全模型："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:183
msgid ""
"Node exporter: TLS encryption and client certificate based authentication"
msgstr "Node 导出器：TLS 加密和基于客户端证书的身份验证"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/monitoring.adoc:184
