"| Debian | libopenscap8 | scap-security-guide-debian\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:20
msgid ""
"RHEL 7 and compatible systems provide a [package]``scap-security-guide`` "
"package, which contains outdated contents.  You are advised to use the "
"[package]``scap-security-guide-redhat`` package you will find in the "
"{productname} Client Tools."
msgstr ""
"RHEL 7 和兼容系统提供了一个 [package]``scap-security-guide`` 软件包，其中包含"
"已过时的内容。建议您使用 {productname} 客户端工具中的 [package]``scap-"
"security-guide-redhat`` 软件包。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:21
msgid ""
"{suse} provides the [package]``scap-security-guide`` package for different "
"openscap profiles.  In the current version of [package]``scap-security-"
"guide``, {suse} supports the following profiles:"
msgstr ""
"{suse} 为不同的 openscap 配置文件提供了 [package]``scap-security-guide`` 软件"
"包。在当前版本的 [package]``scap-security-guide`` 中，{suse} 支持以下配置文"
"件："

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:22
msgid "DISA STIG profile for {sles} 12 and 15"
msgstr "适用于 {sles} 12 和 15 的 DISA STIG 配置文件"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:23
msgid "PCI-DSS profile for {sles} 12 and 15"
msgstr "适用于 {sles} 12 和 15 的 PCI-DSS 配置文件"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:24
msgid "HIPAA profile for {sles} 12 and 15"
msgstr "适用于 {sles} 12 和 15 的 HIPAA 配置文件"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Other profiles, like the CIS profile, are community supplied and not "
"officially supported by {suse}."
msgstr ""
"其他配置文件（例如 CIS 配置文件）由社区提供，{suse} 不为其提供官方支持。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:26
msgid ""
"For Non-{suse} operating systems the included profiles are community "
"supplied.  They are not officially supported by {suse}."
msgstr ""
"对于非 {suse} 操作系统，包含的配置文件由社区提供。{suse} 不为其提供官方支持。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "OpenSCAP Content Files"
msgstr "OpenSCAP 内容文件"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:28
msgid ""
"OpenSCAP uses SCAP content files to define test rules.  These content files "
"are created based on the XCCDF or OVAL standards.  In addition to the SCAP "
"Security Guide, you can download publicly available content files and "
"customize it to your requirements.  You can install the SCAP Security Guide "
"package for default content file templates.  Alternatively, if you are "
"familiar with XCCDF or OVAL, you can create your own content files."
msgstr ""
"OpenSCAP 使用 SCAP 内容文件来定义测试规则。这些内容文件是根据 XCCDF 或 OVAL "
"标准创建的。除了 SCAP 安全指南之外，您还可以下载公开的内容文件并根据要求对其"
"进行自定义。可为默认内容文件模板安装 SCAP 安全指南软件包。或者，如果您熟悉 "
"XCCDF 或 OVAL 的话，可以创建自己的内容文件。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:29
msgid ""
"We recommend you use templates to create your SCAP content files.  If you "
"create and use your own custom content files, you do so at your own risk.  "
"If your system becomes damaged through the use of custom content files, you "
"might not be supported by {suse}."
msgstr ""
"我们建议您使用模板来创建自己的 SCAP 内容文件。如果您创建并使用自己的自定义内"
"容文件，需要自负风险。如果您的系统因使用自定义内容文件而损坏，{suse} 可能不会"
"为您提供支持。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:30
msgid ""
"When you have created your content files, you need to transfer the file to "
"the client.  You can do this in the same way as you move any other file, "
"using physical storage media, or across a network with Salt (for example, "
"https://docs.saltproject.io/en/latest/ref/cli/salt-cp.html[salt-cp] or the "
"https://docs.saltproject.io/en/latest/ref/file_server/index.html[Salt File "
"Server]), [command]``ftp`` or [command]``scp``."
msgstr ""
"创建内容文件后，需要将该文件传输到客户端。可以像移动任何其他文件一样，使用物"
"理储存媒体传输该文件，或者使用 Salt（例如 https://docs.saltproject.io/en/"
"latest/ref/cli/salt-cp.html[salt-cp] 或 https://docs.saltproject.io/en/"
"latest/ref/file_server/index.html[Salt 文件服务器]）在网络上通过 "
"[command]``ftp`` 或 [command]``scp`` 传输该文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:31
msgid ""
"We recommend that you create a package to distribute content files to "
"clients that you are managing with {productname}.  Packages can be signed "
"and verified to ensure their integrity.  For more information, see xref:"
"administration:custom-channels.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"我们建议您创建一个软件包以将内容文件分发到使用 {productname} 管理的客户端。可"
"将软件包签名并对其进行校验以确保其完整性。有关详细信息，请参见 xref:"
"administration:custom-channels.adoc[]。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Find OpenSCAP profiles"
msgstr "查找 OpenSCAP 配置文件"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:33
msgid ""
"Different operating systems make available different OpenSCAP content files "
"and profiles. One content file may contain more than one profile."
msgstr ""
"不同的操作系统提供不同的 OpenSCAP 内容文件和配置文件。一个内容文件可以包含多"
"个配置文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:34
msgid ""
"On RPM-based operating systems, use this command to determine the location "
"of the available SCAP files:"
msgstr "在基于 RPM 的操作系统上，可使用以下命令确定可用 SCAP 文件的位置："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "rpm -ql <scap-security-guide-package-name-from-table>\n"
msgstr "rpm -ql <表中的 SCAP 安全指南软件包名称>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:36
msgid ""
"On DEB-based operating systems, use this command to determine the location "
"of the available SCAP files:"
msgstr "在基于 DEB 的操作系统上，可使用以下命令确定可用 SCAP 文件的位置："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "dpkg -L <scap-security-guide-package-name-from-table>\n"
msgstr "dpkg -L <表中的 SCAP 安全指南软件包名称>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/openscap.adoc:38
msgid ""
"When you have identified one SCAP content file that suits your needs, list "
