#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Managing Disk Space"
msgstr "管理磁盘空间"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Running out of disk space can have a severe impact on the {productname} "
"database and file structure which, in some cases, is not recoverable."
msgstr ""
"磁盘空间不足可能会对 {productname} 数据库和文件结构造成严重影响，在某些情况"
"下，这种影响不可恢复。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:3
msgid ""
"{productname} monitors some directories for free disk space.  You can modify "
"which directories are monitored, and the warnings that are created.  All "
"settings are configured in the [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` configuration "
"file."
msgstr ""
"{productname} 会监视某些目录的可用磁盘空间。您可以修改受监视的目录和创建的警"
"告。所有设置都在 [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` 配置文件中配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:4
msgid ""
"When the available space in one of the monitored directories falls below a "
"warning threshold, a message is sent to the configured email address and a "
"notification is shown at the top of the sign-in page."
msgstr ""
"当某个受监视目录的可用空间低于警告阈值时，会向配置的电子邮件地址发送一条消"
"息，并在登录页面顶部显示一条通知。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "Monitored Directories"
msgstr "受监视的目录"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:6
msgid "By default, {productname} monitors these directories:"
msgstr "{productname} 默认监视以下目录："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:7
msgid "[path]``/var/lib/pgsql``"
msgstr "[path]``/var/lib/pgsql``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:8
msgid "[path]``/var/spacewalk``"
msgstr "[path]``/var/spacewalk``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:9
msgid "[path]``/var/cache``"
msgstr "[path]``/var/cache``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:10
msgid "[path]``/srv``"
msgstr "[path]``/srv``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:11
msgid ""
"You can change which directories are monitored with the "
"[systemitem]``spacecheck_dirs`` parameter.  You can specify multiple "
"directories by separating them with a space."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 [systemitem]``spacecheck_dirs`` 参数更改受监视的目录。可以指定多个"
"目录并用空格将其分隔。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacecheck_dirs = /var/lib/pgsql /var/spacewalk /var/cache /srv\n"
msgstr "spacecheck_dirs = /var/lib/pgsql /var/spacewalk /var/cache /srv\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thresholds"
msgstr "阈值"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:15
msgid ""
"By default, {productname} creates a warning when a monitored directory has "
"less than 10% of total space available.  A critical alert is created when a "
"monitored directory falls below 5% space available."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，当受监视目录的可用空间少于总可用空间的 10% 时，{productname} 会创"
"建警告。当受监视目录的可用空间低于总可用空间的 5% 时，将创建关键警报。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:16
msgid ""
"You can change these alert thresholds with the "
"[systemitem]``spacecheck_free_alert`` and "
"[systemitem]``spacecheck_free_critical`` parameters."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 [systemitem]``spacecheck_free_alert`` 和 "
"[systemitem]``spacecheck_free_critical`` 参数更改这些警报阈值。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"spacecheck_free_alert = 10\n"
"spacecheck_free_critical = 5\n"
msgstr ""
"spacecheck_free_alert = 10\n"
"spacecheck_free_critical = 5\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shut Down Services"
msgstr "关闭服务"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:20
msgid ""
"By default, {productname} shuts down the spacewalk services when the "
"critical alert threshold is reached."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，当达到关键警报阈值时，{productname} 会关闭 spacewalk 服务。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:21
msgid ""
"You can change this behavior with the [systemitem]``spacecheck_shutdown`` "
"parameter.  A value of ``true`` enables the shut down feature.  Any other "
"value disables it."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 [systemitem]``spacecheck_shutdown`` 参数更改此行为。``true`` 值启"
"用关闭功能。任何其他值禁用关闭功能。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacecheck_shutdown = true\n"
msgstr "spacecheck_shutdown = true\n"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Disable Space Checking"
msgstr "禁用空间检查"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:25
msgid ""
"The space checking tool is enabled by default.  You can disable it entirely "
"with these commands:"
msgstr "默认已启用空间检查工具。您可以使用以下命令完全禁用此工具："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"systemctl stop spacewalk-diskcheck.timer\n"
"systemctl disable spacewalk-diskcheck.timer\n"
msgstr ""
"systemctl stop spacewalk-diskcheck.timer\n"
"systemctl disable spacewalk-diskcheck.timer\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/space-management.adoc:27
msgid ""
"Disabling the [literal]``spacewalk-diskcheck.timer`` will stop periodic "
"email alerts if the alert threshold is reached, but the warning notification "
"will still appear at the top of the sign-in page."
msgstr ""
"禁用 [literal]``spacewalk-diskcheck.timer`` 后，如果达到警报阈值，将停止发送"
"定期电子邮件警报，但警告通知仍会显示在登录页面的顶部。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "HTTP Strict Transport Security"
msgstr "HTTP 严格传输安全性"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:2
msgid ""
"HTTP Strict Transport Security (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/"
"HTTP/Headers/Strict-Transport-Security[HSTS]) is a policy mechanism that "
"helps to protect websites against man-in-the-middle attacks such as protocol "
"downgrade attacks and cookie hijacking."
msgstr ""
"HTTP 严格传输安全性 (https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/"
"Headers/Strict-Transport-Security[HSTS]) 是帮助防范网站遭受中间人攻击（例如协"
"议降级攻击和 Cookie 劫持）的策略机制。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:3
msgid ""
"{productname} allows enabling HSTS, to enable it for a {productname} Server:"
msgstr ""
"{productname} 允许启用 HSTS。要为 {productname} Server 启用 HSTS，请执行以下"
"操作："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:4
msgid "Edit `/etc/apache2/conf.d/zz-spacewalk-www.conf`"
msgstr "编辑 `/etc/apache2/conf.d/zz-spacewalk-www.conf`"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:5
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Uncomment the line `# Header always set Strict-Transport-Security \"max-"
"age=63072000; includeSubDomains\"`"
msgstr ""
"取消注释 `# Header always set Strict-Transport-Security \"max-age=63072000; "
"includeSubDomains\"` 行"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:6
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:10
msgid "Restart Apache with `systemctl restart apache2`"
msgstr "使用 `systemctl restart apache2` 重启动 Apache"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:7
msgid "To enable it for {productname} Proxies:"
msgstr "要为 {productname} Proxy 启用 HSTS，请执行以下操作："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:8
msgid "Edit `/etc/apache2/conf.d/spacewalk-proxy.conf`"
msgstr "编辑 `/etc/apache2/conf.d/spacewalk-proxy.conf`"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-hsts.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**IMPORTANT:** Once HSTS is enabled while using the default SSL certificate generated by {productname} or a self-signed certificate, browsers will refuse to connect using HTTPS unless the CA used to sign such certificates is trusted by the browser.\n"
"If you are using the SSL certificate generated by {productname}, you can trust it by importing the file located at `http://<SERVER-HOSTNAME>/pub/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT` to the browsers of all users.\n"
msgstr ""
"**重要说明：**在使用 {productname} 生成的默认 SSL 证书或自我签名证书的情况下启用 HSTS 后，浏览器将拒绝使用 HTTPS 进行连接，除非用于为此类证书签名的 CA 受浏览器的信任。\n"
"如果您使用的是 {productname} 生成的 SSL 证书，可以通过将 `http://<服务器主机名>/pub/RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT` 中的文件导入到所有用户的浏览器来信任该证书。\n"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Import SSL Certificates"
msgstr "导入 SSL 证书"

#. By default, {productname} uses a self-signed certificate.
#. For additional security, you can import a custom certificate, signed by a third party certificate authority (CA).
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:2
msgid ""
"This section covers how to configure SSL certificate for new {productname} "
"installation, and how to replace existing certificates."
msgstr ""
"本节介绍如何为新的 {productname} 安装配置 SSL 证书，以及如何替换现有证书。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:3
msgid "Before you begin, ensure you have:"
msgstr "在开始之前，请确保已准备好："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:4
msgid ""
"A certificate authority (CA) SSL public certificate.  If you are using a CA "
"chain, all intermediate CAs must also be available."
msgstr ""
"一个证书颁发机构 (CA) SSL 公共证书。如果您使用 CA 链，则所有中间 CA 也必须可"
"用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:5
msgid "An SSL server private key"
msgstr "一个 SSL 服务器私用密钥"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:6
msgid "An SSL server certificate"
msgstr "一个 SSL 服务器证书"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:7
msgid "All files must be in PEM format."
msgstr "所有文件必须采用 PEM 格式。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:8
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The host name of the SSL server certificate must match the fully "
#| "qualified host name of the machine you deploy them on.  You can set the "
#| "host names in the ``X509v3 Subject Alternative Name`` section of the "
#| "certificate.  You can also list multiple host names if your environment "
#| "requires it."
msgid ""
"The host name of the SSL server certificate must match the fully qualified "
"host name of the machine you deploy them on.  You can set the host names in "
"the [literal]``X509v3 Subject Alternative Name`` section of the "
"certificate.  You can also list multiple host names if your environment "
"requires it.  Supported Key types are [literal]``RSA`` and [literal]``EC`` "
"(Elliptic Curve)."
msgstr ""
"SSL 服务器证书的主机名必须与其部署到的计算机的完全限定主机名匹配。可以在证书"
"的 ``X509v3 Subject Alternative Name`` 部分中设置主机名。还可以根据环境的需要"
"列出多个主机名。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Third-party authorities commonly use intermediate CAs to sign requested "
"server certificates.  In this case, all CAs in the chain are required to be "
"available.  If there is no extra parameter or option available to specify "
"intermediate CAs, take care that all CAs (Root CA and intermediate CAs) are "
"stored in one file."
msgstr ""
"第三方颁发机构通常使用中间 CA 来为请求的服务器证书签名。在这种情况下，链中的"
"所有 CA 都必须可用。如果没有额外的参数或选项可用于指定中间 CA，请注意所有 CA"
"（根 CA 和中间 CA）都将储存在一个文件中。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:10
