"根据 xref:installation-and-upgrade:install-intro.adoc[] 中的说明安装 "
"{productname} Server。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Complete the initial setup according to xref:installation-and-upgrade:server-"
"setup.adoc[]."
msgstr "根据 xref:installation-and-upgrade:server-setup.adoc[] 完成初始设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:15
msgid ""
"At the command prompt, point the SSL environment variables to the "
"certificate file locations:"
msgstr "在命令提示符下，将 SSL 环境变量指向证书文件位置："

