msgstr "为新的 Proxy 安装导入证书"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:22
msgid ""
"By default, {productname} Proxy uses a self-signed certificate.  After you "
"have completed the initial setup, you can replace the default certificate "
"with an imported certificate."
msgstr ""
"{productname} Proxy 默认使用自我签名证书。完成初始设置后，您可以将默认证书替"
"换为导入的证书。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Import Certificates on a New {productname} Proxy"
msgstr "过程：在新的 {productname} Proxy 上导入证书"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:24
msgid ""
"Install the {productname} Proxy according to the instructions in xref:"
"installation-and-upgrade:install-intro.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"根据xref:installation-and-upgrade:install-intro.adoc[]中的说明安装 "
"{productname} Proxy。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Complete the initial setup according to xref:installation-and-upgrade:proxy-"
"setup.adoc[]."
msgstr "根据xref:installation-and-upgrade:proxy-setup.adoc[]完成初始设置。"

#. type: Plain text
