msgstr "在命令提示符下，运行："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "configure-proxy.sh\n"
msgstr "configure-proxy.sh\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:28
msgid ""
"At the ``Do you want to import existing certificates?`` prompt, type kbd:[y]."
msgstr "出现``您要导入现有证书吗？``提示时，键入 kbd:[y]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:29
msgid "Follow the prompts to complete setup."
msgstr "按照提示完成设置。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:30
msgid ""
"Use the same certificate authority to sign all server certificates for "
"servers and proxies.  Certificates signed with different CAs do not match."
msgstr ""
"使用同一证书颁发机构为服务器和代理的所有服务器证书签名。使用不同 CA 签名的证"
"书将不匹配。"

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Replace Certificates"
msgstr "替换证书"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:32
msgid ""
"You can replace active certificates on your {productname} installation with "
"a new certificate.  To replace the certificates, you can replace the "
"installed CA certificate with the new CA, and then update the database."
msgstr ""
"您可以将 {productname} 安装中的活动证书替换为新证书。要替换证书，可以将已安装"
"的 CA 证书替换为新 CA，然后更新数据库。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Replacing Existing Certificates"
msgstr "过程：替换现有证书"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:34
msgid ""
"On the {productname} Server, at the command prompt, call the command `mgr-"
"ssl-cert-setup` and provide the certificates as parameters:"
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} Server 上的命令提示符下，调用命令 `mgr-ssl-cert-setup` 并提"
"供证书作为参数："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-ssl-cert-setup --root-ca-file=<Path_to_Root_CA_Certificate> --server-cert-file=<Server_Cert_File> --server-key-file=<Server_Key_File>\n"
msgstr "mgr-ssl-cert-setup --root-ca-file=<根 CA 证书的路径> --server-cert-file=<服务器证书文件> --server-key-file=<服务器密钥文件>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:36
msgid ""
"Intermediate CAs can either be available in the file which is specified with "
"`--root-ca-file` or specified as extra options with `--intermediate-ca-"
"file`.  The `--intermediate-ca-file` option can be specified multiple "
"times.  This command performs a number of tests on the provided files to "
"test if they are valid and can be used for the requested use case."
msgstr ""
"中间 CA 可以在使用 `--root-ca-file` 指定的文件中提供，也可以使用 `--"
"intermediate-ca-file` 作为附加选项来指定。可以多次指定 `--intermediate-ca-"
"file` 选项。此命令将对提供的文件执行一些测试，以测试它们是否有效并可用于请求"
"的用例。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:37
msgid "Restart services to pick up the changes:"
msgstr "重启动服务以应用更改："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/ssl-certs-imported.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"spacewalk-service stop\n"
"systemctl restart postgresql.service\n"
"spacewalk-service start\n"
msgstr ""
"spacewalk-service stop\n"
"systemctl restart postgresql.service\n"
"spacewalk-service start\n"

