#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:errata-queue-default[]"
msgstr "menu:errata-queue-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:31
msgid ""
"Queues automatic updates (patches) for servers that are configured to "
"receive them."
msgstr "为配置为接收自动更新（补丁）的服务器将这些更新（补丁）排队。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:gatherer-matcher-default[]"
msgstr "menu:gatherer-matcher-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:33
msgid ""
"Gather virtual host data by running Virtual Host Gatherer configured in "
"Virtual Host Managers.  After updated data are available, the Subscription "
"Matcher job is run."
msgstr ""
"通过运行在虚拟主机管理器中配置的虚拟主机收集器，来收集虚拟主机数据。当有更新"
"的数据后，订阅匹配器作业即会运行。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:kickstart-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:kickstart-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:35
msgid "Cleans up stale {kickstart} session data."
msgstr "清理过时的 {kickstart} 会话数据。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:kickstartfile-sync-default[]"
msgstr "menu:kickstartfile-sync-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:37
msgid ""
"Generates Cobbler files corresponding to {kickstart} profiles created by the "
"configuration wizard."
msgstr "生成与配置向导创建的 {kickstart} 配置文件对应的 Cobbler 文件。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:mgr-forward-registration-default[]"
msgstr "menu:mgr-forward-registration-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:39
msgid ""
"Synchronizes client registration data with {scc}.  By default, new, changed, "
"or deleted client data are forwarded.  To disable synchronization set in "
"[path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf``, run:"
msgstr ""
"将客户端注册数据与 {scc} 同步。默认会转发新的、已更改的或已删除的客户端数据。"
"要禁用 [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf`` 中设置的同步，请运行："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "server.susemanager.forward_registration = 0\n"
msgstr "server.susemanager.forward_registration = 0\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:mgr-sync-refresh-default[]"
msgstr "menu:mgr-sync-refresh-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:42
msgid ""
"Synchronizes with {scc} (``mgr-sync-refresh``).  By default, all custom "
"channels are also synchronized as part of this task.  For more information "
"about custom channel synchronization, see xref:administration:custom-"
"channels.adoc#_custom_channel_synchronization[]."
msgstr ""
"与 {scc} 保持同步 (``mgr-sync-refresh``)。默认情况下，在此任务执行过程中也会"
"同步所有自定义通道。有关自定义通道同步的详细信息，请参见 xref:administration:"
"custom-channels.adoc#_custom_channel_synchronization[]。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:minion-action-chain-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:minion-action-chain-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:44
msgid "Cleans up outdated action chain data."
msgstr "清理过时的操作链数据。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:minion-action-cleanup-defaul:[]"
msgstr "menu:minion-action-cleanup-defaul:[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:46
msgid ""
"Deletes stale client action data from the file system.  First it tries to "
"complete any possibly unfinished actions by looking up the corresponding "
"results stored in the {salt} job cache.  An unfinished action can occur if "
"the server has missed the results of the action.  For successfully completed "
"actions it removes artifacts such as executed script files."
msgstr ""
"从文件系统中删除过时的客户端操作数据。首先，此任务组会尝试通过查找存储在 "
"{salt} 作业缓存中的相应结果，来完成任何可能未完成的操作。如果服务器遗漏了操作"
"结果，就可能发生操作未完成的情况。对于成功完成的操作，此任务组会去除已执行的"
"脚本文件等项目。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:minion-checkin-default[]"
msgstr "menu:minion-checkin-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:48
msgid "Performs a regular check-in on clients."
msgstr "在客户端上执行常规的签入。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:notifications-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:notifications-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:50
msgid "Cleans up expired notification messages."
msgstr "清理失效的通知消息。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:package-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:package-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:52
msgid "Deletes stale package files from the file system."
msgstr "从文件系统中删除过时的软件包文件。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:reboot-action-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:reboot-action-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:54
msgid ""
"Any reboot actions pending for more than six hours are marked as failed and "
"associated data is cleaned up from the database.  For more information on "
"scheduling reboot actions, see xref:reference:systems/system-details/sd-"
"provisioning.adoc#sd-power-management[]."
msgstr ""
"任何超过六个小时未处理的重引导操作都将标记为失败，数据库中的关联数据将被清"
"理。有关安排重引导操作的详细信息，请参见 xref:reference:systems/system-"
"details/sd-provisioning.adoc#sd-power-management[]。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:sandbox-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:sandbox-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:56
msgid ""
"Cleans up Sandbox configuration files and channels that are older than the "
"__sandbox_lifetime__ configuration parameter (3 days by default).  Sandbox "
"files are those imported from systems or files under development.  For more "
"information, see xref:reference:systems/system-details/sd-configuration."
"adoc#sd-config-add-files[]."
msgstr ""
"清理超过 __sandbox_lifetime__ 配置参数值（默认值为 3 天）的沙箱配置文件和通"
"道。沙箱文件是从系统导入的文件或正在开发的文件。有关详细信息，请参见 xref:"
"reference:systems/system-details/sd-configuration.adoc#sd-config-add-"
"files[]。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:session-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:session-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:58
msgid ""
"Cleans up stale Web interface sessions, typically data that is temporarily "
"stored when a user logs in and then closes the browser before logging out."
msgstr ""
"清理过时的 Web 界面会话，这通常是用户登录之后，在注销之前关闭浏览器时临时储存"
"的数据。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:ssh-push-default[]"
msgstr "menu:ssh-push-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:60
msgid ""
"Prompts clients to check in with {productname} via SSH if they are "
"configured with a `SSH Push` contact method."
msgstr ""
"如果为客户端配置了 ``SSH Push`` 联系方法，则提示客户端通过 SSH 来与 "
"{productname} 通讯。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:61
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:system-profile-refresh-default[]"
msgstr "menu:system-profile-refresh-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:62
msgid ""
"Runs a hardware refresh on all systems.  This happens only monthly and can "
"increase load on the {productname} Server.  The job uses xref:specialized-"
"guides:salt/salt-rate-limiting.adoc[Salt Rate Limiting].  For tuning the "
"batch size, see xref:specialized-guides:large-deployments/tuning.adoc#java-"
"salt-batch-size[]."
msgstr ""
"在所有系统上执行硬件刷新。此任务组每月只执行一次，可能会增加 {productname} 服"
"务器上的负荷。该作业会使用 xref:specialized-guides:salt/salt-rate-limiting."
"adoc[Salt 率限制]。如果要调整批次大小，请参见 xref:specialized-guides:large-"
"deployments/tuning.adoc#java-salt-batch-size[]。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:token-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:token-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:64
msgid ""
"Deletes expired repository tokens that are used by {salt} clients to "
"download packages and metadata."
msgstr "删除 {salt} 客户端用来下载软件包和元数据的已失效储存库令牌。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:update-payg-default[]"
msgstr "menu:update-payg-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:66
msgid "Collects authentication data from configure {payg} cloud instances."
msgstr "从配置的 {payg} 云实例收集身份验证数据。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:update-reporting-default[]"
msgstr "menu:update-reporting-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:68
msgid "Updates the local Reporting Database."
msgstr "更新本地报告数据库。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:update-reporting-hub-default[]"
msgstr "menu:update-reporting-hub-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:70
msgid ""
"Collects all reporting data from peripheral {productname} Server and update "
"the Hub Reporting Database."
msgstr ""
"从外围 {productname} 服务器收集所有报告数据，并更新 Hub Reporting 数据库。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "menu:uuid-cleanup-default[]"
msgstr "menu:uuid-cleanup-default[]"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/task-schedules.adoc:72
msgid "Cleans up outdated UUID records."
msgstr "清理过时的 UUID 记录。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Autoinstallation"
msgstr "自动安装查错"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Depending on your base channel, new autoinstallation profiles might be "
"subscribed to a channel that is missing required packages."
msgstr "根据您的基础通道，新的自动安装配置文件可能会订阅缺少必需软件包的通道。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:3
msgid "For autoinstallation to work, these packages are required:"
msgstr "要使自动安装可以正常进行，必须提供以下软件包："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:4
msgid "[package]``pyOpenSSL``"
msgstr "[package]``pyOpenSSL``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:5
msgid "[package]``rhnlib``"
msgstr "[package]``rhnlib``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:6
msgid "[package]``libxml2-python``"
msgstr "[package]``libxml2-python``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:7
msgid "[package]``spacewalk-koan``"
msgstr "[package]``spacewalk-koan``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:8
msgid "To resolve this issue, check these things first:"
msgstr "为了解决此问题，请先进行以下检查："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Check that the tools software channel related to the base channel in your "
"autoinstallation profile is available to your organization and your user."
msgstr ""
"检查是否为您的组织和用户提供了与自动安装配置文件中的基础通道相关的工具软件通"
"道。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Check that the tools channel is available to your {productname} as a child "
"channel."
msgstr "检查是否为您的 {productname} 提供了工具通道作为子通道。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-autoinstallation.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Check that the required packages and any dependencies are available in the "
"associated channels.:"
msgstr "检查关联的通道中是否提供了所需的软件包和任何依赖项。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Bare Metal Systems"
msgstr "裸机系统查错"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If a bare metal system on the network is not automatically added to the "
"[guilabel]``Systems`` list, check these things first:"
msgstr ""
"如果网络中的裸机系统不会自动添加到[guilabel]``系统``列表中，请先进行以下检"
"查："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:3
msgid "You must have the [path]``pxe-default-image`` package installed."
msgstr "您必须已安装 [path]``pxe-default-image`` 软件包。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:4
msgid ""
"File paths and parameters must be configured correctly. Check that the "
"[path]``vmlinuz0`` and [path]``initrd0.img`` files, which are provided by "
"[path]``pxe-default-image``, are in the locations specified in the "
"[path]``rhn.conf`` configuration file."
msgstr ""
"必须正确配置文件路径和参数。检查 [path]``pxe-default-image`` 提供的 "
"[path]``vmlinuz0`` 和 [path]``initrd0.img`` 文件是否位于 [path]``rhn.conf`` "
"配置文件中指定的位置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:5
msgid ""
"Ensure the networking equipment connecting the bare metal system to the "
"{productname} server is working correctly, and that you can reach the "
"{productname} server IP address from the server."
msgstr ""
"确保将裸机系统连接到 {productname} 服务器的网络设备可正常运行，并且您可以从该"
"服务器访问 {productname} 服务器 IP 地址。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:6
msgid ""
"The bare metal system to be provisioned must have PXE booting enabled in the "
"boot sequence, and must not be attempting to boot an operating system."
msgstr ""
"要置备的裸机系统必须在引导序列中启用 PXE 引导，并且必须未在尝试引导操作系统。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:7
msgid ""
"The DHCP server must be responding to DHCP requests during boot. Check the "
"PXE boot messages to ensure that:"
msgstr "引导期间，DHCP 服务器必须响应 DHCP 请求。检查 PXE 引导消息，确保："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:8
msgid "the DHCP server is assigning the expected IP address"
msgstr "DHCP 服务器指派的是预期的 IP 地址"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:9
msgid ""
"the DHCP server is assigning the the {productname} server IP address as "
"[option]``next-server`` for booting."
msgstr ""
"DHCP 服务器为要引导的 [option]``next-server`` 指派的是 {productname} 服务器 "
"IP 地址。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:10
msgid "Ensure Cobbler is running, and that the Discovery feature is enabled."
msgstr "确保 Cobbler 正在运行，并且已启用发现功能。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:11
msgid ""
"If you see a blue Cobbler menu shortly after booting, discovery has "
"started.  If it does not complete successfully, temporarily disable "
"automatic shutdown to help diagnose the problem. To disable automatic "
"shutdown:"
msgstr ""
"如果您在引导后看到短暂显示的蓝色 Cobbler 菜单，则说明发现功能已启动。如果该过"
"程未成功完成，请暂时禁用自动关闭以帮助诊断问题。要禁用自动关闭，请执行以下操"
"作："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Select [option]``pxe-default-profile`` in the Cobbler menu with the arrow "
"keys, and press the Tab key before the timer expires."
msgstr ""
"使用方向键在 Cobbler 菜单中选择 [option]``pxe-default-profile``，然后在计时器"
"到期前按 Tab 键。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:13
msgid ""
"Add the kernel boot parameter [option]``spacewalk-finally=running`` using "
"the integrated editor, and press Enter to continue booting."
msgstr ""
"使用集成编辑器添加内核引导参数 [option]``spacewalk-finally=running``，然后按 "
"Enter 继续引导。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Enter a shell with the username [option]``root`` and password "
"[option]``linux`` to continue debugging."
msgstr ""
"使用用户名 [option]``root`` 和口令 [option]``linux`` 进入外壳继续调试。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bare-metal-systems.adoc:15
msgid ""
"Due to a technical limitation, it is not possible to reliably distinguish a "
"new bare metal system from a system that has previously been discovered.  "
"Therefore, we recommended that you do not power on bare metal systems "
"multiple times, as this results in duplicate profiles."
msgstr ""
"受技术所限，我们无法可靠地区分新裸机系统与先前已发现的系统。因此，建议您不要"
"多次启动裸机系统，因为这会导致产生重复的配置文件。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Bootstrap Repository for End-of-Life Products"
msgstr "对生命周期已结束产品的引导储存库进行查错"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:2
msgid ""
"When supported products are synchronized, bootstrap repositories are "
"automatically created and regenerated on the {productname} Server.  When a "
"product reaches end-of-life and becomes unsupported, bootstrap repositories "
"must be created manually if you want to continue using the product."
msgstr ""
"同步受支持的产品时，会自动在 {productname} Server 上创建及重新生成引导储存"
"库。当产品到达生命周期结束日期且不再受支持时，如果您要继续使用此产品，就必须"
"手动创建引导储存库。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:3
msgid ""
"For more information about bootstrap repositories, see xref:client-"
"configuration:bootstrap-repository.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关引导储存库的详细信息，请参见 xref:client-configuration:bootstrap-"
"repository.adoc[]。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:4
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Creating Bootstrap Repositories for End-Of-Life Products"
msgstr "过程：创建生命周期已结束产品的引导储存库"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:5
msgid ""
"At the command prompt on the {productname} Server, as root, list the "
"available unsupported bootstrap repositories with the [option]``--force`` "
"option, for example:"
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} Server 上的命令提示符下，以 root 身份使用 [option]``--"
"force``选项列出不受支持的可用引导储存库，例如："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"mgr-create-bootstrap-repo --list --force\n"
"1. SLE-12-SP2-x86_64\n"
"2. SLE-12-SP3-x86_64\n"
msgstr ""
"mgr-create-bootstrap-repo --list --force\n"
"1. SLE-12-SP2-x86_64\n"
"2. SLE-12-SP3-x86_64\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:7
msgid ""
"Create the bootstrap repository, using the appropriate repository name as "
"the product label:"
msgstr "创建引导储存库，并使用适当的储存库名称作为产品标签："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "mgr-create-bootstrap-repo --create SLE-12-SP2-x86_64 --force\n"
msgstr "mgr-create-bootstrap-repo --create SLE-12-SP2-x86_64 --force\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-bootstrap-repo-for-eol-products.adoc:9
msgid ""
"If you do not want to create bootstrap repositories manually, you can check "
"whether LTSS is available for the product and bootstrap repository you need."
msgstr ""
"如果您不想手动创建引导储存库，可以检查您需要的产品和引导储存库是否有 LTSS。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-cloned-salt-clients.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Clients Cloned Salt Clients"
msgstr "对克隆的 Salt 客户端进行查错"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-cloned-salt-clients.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you have used your hypervisor clone utility, and attempted to register "
"the cloned Salt client, you might get this error:"
msgstr ""
"如果您曾经使用过超级管理程序克隆实用程序，并尝试注册克隆的 Salt 客户端，您可"
"能会收到以下错误："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-cloned-salt-clients.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid "We're sorry, but the system could not be found.\n"
msgstr "抱歉，找不到该系统。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-cloned-salt-clients.adoc:4
msgid ""
"This is caused by the new, cloned, system having the same machine ID as an "
"existing, registered, system.  You can adjust this manually to correct the "
"error and register the cloned system successfully."
msgstr ""
"发生该错误的原因是新的克隆系统与现有的已注册系统具有相同的计算机 ID。您可以手"
"动调整此数据以修复该错误，然后便可成功注册克隆的系统。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-cloned-salt-clients.adoc:5
msgid ""
"For more information and instructions, see xref:administration:"
"troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息和说明，请参见 xref:administration:troubleshooting/tshoot-"
"registerclones.adoc[]。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-corruptrepo.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Corrupt Repositories"
msgstr "对损坏的储存库进行查错"

#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
