"If you do not know the channel label, you can find it in the {productname} "
"{webui}, by navigating to menu:Software[Channels > Channel Label]."
msgstr ""
"如果您不知道通道标签是什么，可以在 {productname} {webui} 中导航到menu:软件[通"
"道 > 通道标签]找到它。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-corruptrepo.adoc:6
msgid "Regenerate the file from the command line:"
msgstr "从命令行重新生成文件："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-corruptrepo.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacecmd softwarechannel_regenerateyumcache <channel-label>\n"
msgstr "spacecmd softwarechannel_regenerateyumcache <通道标签>\n"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Custom Channel with Conflicting Packages"
msgstr "对包含有冲突软件包的自定义通道进行查错"

#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. Cause: Conflicting packages in custom channel
#. Consequence: Creating bootstrap repo can fail
#. Fix: Separate trees from each other
#. Result: Clean and functional boostrap repo will be created
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:2
msgid ""
"When setting up a custom channel with conflicting packages features such as "
"creating a bootstrap repository can result in undefined behavior and make "
"registering clients fail."
msgstr ""
"设置包含有冲突软件包的自定义通道时，某些功能（例如创建引导储存库）可能会导致"
"未定义的行为，并使客户端注册失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:3
msgid ""
"For example, conflicting packages with higher version numbers could be "
"included into the bootstrap repository.  Such packages (for example, "
"[package]``python3-zmq`` or [package]``zeromq``) may corrupt the creation of "
"the bootstrap repository or cause issues during bootstrap of the client."
msgstr ""
"例如，版本号较高的有冲突软件包可能会包含在引导储存库中。此类软件包（例如 "
"[package]``python3-zmq`` 或 [package]``zeromq``）可能会导致创建引导储存库时出"
"错，或者在客户端引导期间导致问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:4
msgid ""
"When the custom channel (for example, an EPEL channel) is added below the "
"parent vendor channel, issues with conflicting packages cannot be solved "
"directly.  The way how to solve this is to separate the custom channel from "
"the vendor channel.  The custom channel needs to be created in a separate "
"tree.  In case that the custom channel needs to be delivered as a child, "
"such environemnt can be created using Content Lifecycle Management (CLM).  "
"Sources in a CLM project can be added there from different trees.  Using "
"such an approach, the custom channel stays below the parent within the built "
"environment.  However, the vendor channel tree stays without the custom "
"channel and the bootstrap repository.  Then registering clients works "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"在父供应商通道下面添加自定义通道（例如 EPEL 通道）时，无法直接解决软件包冲突"
"问题。此问题的解决方法是将自定义通道与供应商通道分开。需要在单独的树中创建自"
"定义通道。如果需要将自定义通道作为子通道递送，可以使用内容生命周期管理 (CLM) "
"创建此类环境。可以从不同的树添加 CLM 项目中的源。如果使用这种方法，自定义通道"
"将保留在构建的环境中的父项之下。但是，供应商通道树仍然不包含自定义通道和引导"
"储存库。然后可以正常注册客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:5
msgid ""
"When the custom channel with the conflicting packages (salt, zeromq, and so "
"on) is created as a child channel, following steps can help to avoid the "
"issue:"
msgstr ""
"将包含有冲突软件包的自定义通道（salt、zeromq 等）创建为子通道时，以下步骤可能"
"有助于避免该问题："

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Avoiding Conflicting Packages in Custom Channels"
msgstr "过程：避免自定义通道中包含有冲突的软件包"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:7
msgid ""
"Remove the custom channel as a child channel from parent channel.  For more "
"information, see xref:administration:custom-channels."
"adoc#_manage_custom_channels[]."
msgstr ""
"从父通道中去除作为子通道的自定义通道。有关详细信息，请参见 xref:"
"administration:custom-channels.adoc#_manage_custom_channels[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Create the custom channel in a separate tree.  For more information, see "
"xref:administration:custom-channels."
"adoc#_creating_custom_channels_and_repositories[]."
msgstr ""
"在单独的树中创建自定义通道。有关详细信息，请参见 xref:administration:custom-"
"channels.adoc#_creating_custom_channels_and_repositories[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:9
msgid ""
"To get the custom channel as a child channel within Content Lifecycle "
"Management (CLM):"
msgstr ""
"要在内容生命周期管理 (CLM) 中添加作为子通道的自定义通道，请执行以下操作："

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:10
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Content Lifecycle[], and "
"click btn:[Create Project].  Enter [guimenu]``Name`` and [guimenu]``Label``."
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} {webui} 中，导航到menu:内容生命周期[]，然后单击 btn:[创建项"
"目]。输入[guimenu]``名称``和[guimenu]``标签``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:11
msgid ""
"Attach Source to the project.  Use the needed vendor channels and the custom "
"channel.  // (sharing example using CentOS8)"
msgstr ""
"将源挂接到项目。使用所需的供应商通道和自定义通道。//（分享使用 CentOS8 的示"
"例）"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:12
msgid "Add environment into the Project.  // example using CentOS8"
msgstr "将环境添加到项目中。// 使用 CentOS8 的示例"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:13
msgid ""
"To build the environment click the btn:[Build] button.  This creates an "
"environment with vendor and custom channels that can be associated with an "
"activation key and used to bootstrap the client."
msgstr ""
"要构建环境，请单击 btn:[构建] 按钮。这会创建一个包含供应商通道和自定义通道的"
"环境，这些通道可与激活密钥相关联并用于引导客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Important note: In the CLM project, it is recommend to add a filter, which "
"excludes the problematic or conflicting packages.  Otherwise the conflicting "
"packages with higher version numbers would be installed during the update of "
"the client.  For more information about filtering, see xref:administration:"
"content-lifecycle-examples.adoc#exclude-higher-kernel-version[]."
msgstr ""
"重要说明：在 CLM 项目中，建议添加一个过滤器用于排除有问题或有冲突的软件包。否"
"则会在客户端更新期间安装版本号较高的有冲突软件包。有关过滤的详细信息，请参见 "
"xref:administration:content-lifecycle-examples.adoc#exclude-higher-kernel-"
"version[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:15
msgid ""
"To get the latest patches into the CLM environment (with vendor and custom "
"channel), click the btn:[Build] button in the project.  This is needed to re-"
"built the environment."
msgstr ""
"要将最新补丁添加到 CLM 环境（包含供应商通道和自定义通道），请在项目中单击 "
"btn:[构建] 按钮。需要执行此操作才能重构建环境。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:16
msgid ""
"For more information about CLM, see xref:administration:content-lifecycle."
"adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"有关 CLM 的详细信息，请参见 xref:administration:content-lifecycle.adoc[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-custom-channel.adoc:17
msgid ""
"For another workaround, see https://www.suse.com/releasenotes/x86_64/SUSE-"
"MANAGER/4.2/index.html#_epel_and_salt_packages."
msgstr ""
"有关另一种解决方法，请参见 link:https://www.suse.com/releasenotes/x86_64/"
"SUSE-MANAGER/4.2/index.html#_epel_and_salt_packages[]。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Disabling the FQDNS grain"
msgstr "对禁用 FQDNS grain 时出现的问题进行查错"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:2
msgid ""
"The FQDNS grain returns the list of all the fully qualified DNS services in "
"the system.  Collecting this information is usually a fast process, but if "
"the DNS settings have been misconfigured, it could take a much longer time.  "
"In some cases, the client could become unresponsive, or crash."
msgstr ""
"FQDNS grain 会返回系统中所有完全限定 DNS 服务的列表。通常很快就能完成这些信息"
"的收集，但如果 DNS 设置配置错误，花费的时间可能会长很多。在某些情况下，客户端"
"会变成无响应状态或者会崩溃。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:3
msgid ""
"To prevent this problem, you can disable the FQDNS grain with a Salt flag.  "
"If you disable the grain, you can use a network module to provide FQDNS "
"services, without the risk of the client becoming unresponsive."
msgstr ""
"为了防止发生此问题，您可以使用 Salt 标志来禁用 FQDNS grain。如果禁用 grain，"
"您便可以使用网络模块提供 FQDNS 服务，而不会面临客户端变成无响应状态的风险。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:4
msgid ""
"This only applies to older Salt clients.  If you registered your Salt client "
"recently, the FQDNS grain is disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"这仅适用于较旧的 Salt 客户端。如果您是最近注册 Salt 客户端的，FQDNS grain 默"
"认会禁用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:5
msgid ""
"On the {productname} Server, at the command prompt, use this command to "
"disable the FQDNS grain:"
msgstr ""
"在 {productname} Server 上的命令提示符下，使用以下命令禁用 FQDNS grain："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt '*' state.sls util.mgr_disable_fqdns_grain\n"
msgstr "salt '*' state.sls util.mgr_disable_fqdns_grain\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:7
msgid ""
"This command restarts each client and generate Salt events that the server "
"needs to process.  If you have a large number of clients, you can execute "
"the command in batch mode instead:"
msgstr ""
"此命令会重启动每个客户端并生成服务器需要处理的 Salt 事件。如果您的客户端非常"
"多，可以改用批处理模式执行该命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "salt --batch-size 50 '*' state.sls util.mgr_disable_fqdns_grain\n"
msgstr "salt --batch-size 50 '*' state.sls util.mgr_disable_fqdns_grain\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-disabling-fqdns-grain.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Wait for the batch command to finish executing.  Do not interrupt the "
"process with kbd:[Ctrl+C]."
msgstr "等待批处理命令执行完。请不要按 kbd:[Ctrl+C] 中断该过程。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Disk Space"
msgstr "磁盘空间查错"

#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Running out of disk space can have a severe impact on the {productname} "
"database and file structure which, in most cases, is not recoverable.  "
"{productname} monitors free space in specific directories, and has "
"configurable alerts.  For more on space management, see xref:administration:"
"space-management.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"磁盘空间不足可能会对 {productname} 数据库和文件结构造成严重影响，在大多数情况"
"下，这种影响不可恢复。{productname} 会监视特定目录的可用空间，在有问题时会发"
"出警报（可配置）。有关空间管理的详细信息，请参见 xref:administration:space-"
"management.adoc[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:3
msgid ""
"You can recover disk space by removing unused software channels.  For "
"instructions on how to delete vendor channels, see xref:administration:"
"channel-management.adoc[].  For instructions on how to delete custom "
"channels, see xref:administration:custom-channels.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"可以通过去除未使用的软件通道来恢复磁盘空间。有关如何删除供应商通道的说明，请"
"参见xref:administration:channel-management.adoc[]。有关如何删除自定义通道的说"
"明，请参见 xref:administration:custom-channels.adoc[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:4
msgid ""
"You can also check how often your custom channels are synchronized.  For "
"instructions on how deal with custom channel synchronization, see xref:"
"administration:custom-channels.adoc#_custom_channel_synchronization[]."
msgstr ""
"您还可以检查自定义通道的同步频率。有关如何处理自定义通道同步的说明，请参见 "
"xref:administration:custom-channels.adoc#_custom_channel_synchronization[]。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:5
msgid ""
"You can also recover disk space by cleaning up unused activation keys, "
"content lifecycle projects, and client registrations.  You can also remove "
"redundant database entries:"
msgstr ""
"还可以通过清理未使用的激活密钥、内容生命周期项目和客户端注册来恢复磁盘空间。"
"还可以去除多余的数据库项："

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Resolving Redundant Database Entries"
msgstr "过程：去除多余的数据库项"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:7
msgid ""
"Use the [command]``spacewalk-data-fsck`` command to list any redundant "
"database entries."
msgstr "使用 [command]``spacewalk-data-fsck`` 命令列出所有多余的数据库项。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-diskspace.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Use the [command]``spacewalk-data-fsck --remove`` command to delete them."
msgstr "使用 [command]``spacewalk-data-fsck --remove`` 命令删除这些项。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Firewalls"
msgstr "防火墙查错"

#
#
#
#
#
#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. Cause: User firewall is set to block outgoing traffic by dropping the packet request. During sync with SCC, SUMA waits for an answer on each URL until it times out, eventually causing the entire refresh of the product list to timeout. Applies only to third party (non-SUSE) products, as sync with SCC needs to access locations other than SCC to verify if the if the download location is valid.
#. Consequence: The sync to SCC fails, and the third party products are not shown in the product list.
#. Fix: Configure the firewall to reject requests from SUMA instead of drop (preferred), or configure a firewall on the server (if no ability to change firewall settings)
#. Result: Sync to SCC is either able to reach the URLs required, or rejects the request so that the request fails rather than times out.
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you are using a firewall that blocks outgoing traffic, it can either "
"``REJECT`` or ``DROP`` network requests.  If it is set to ``DROP`` then you "
"might find that synchronizing with the {scc} times out."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用的防火墙阻止了传出流量，它可能会``拒绝``或``丢弃``网络请求。如果该"
"防火墙设置为``丢弃``，则与 {scc} 同步可能会超时。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:3
msgid ""
"This occurs because the synchronization process needs to access third-party "
"repositories that provide packages for non-{suse} clients, and not just the "
"{scc}.  When the {productname} Server attempts to reach these repositories "
"to check that they are valid, the firewall drops the requests, and the "
"synchronization continues to wait for the response until it times out."
msgstr ""
"之所以发生这种情况，是因为同步进程需要访问为非 {suse} 客户端（而不仅仅是 "
"{scc}）提供软件包的第三方储存库。当 {productname} Server 尝试访问这些储存库以"
"检查它们是否有效时，防火墙会丢弃请求，并且同步进程会继续等待响应，直到超时。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:4
msgid ""
"If this occurs, the synchronization takes a long time before it fails, and "
"your non-{suse} products are not shown in the product list."
msgstr ""
"如果发生这种情况，同步将持续很长时间，然后失败，并且您的非 {suse} 产品不会显"
"示在产品列表中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:5
msgid "You can fix this problem in several different ways."
msgstr "可以通过多种不同的方法解决此问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:6
msgid ""
"The simplest method is to configure your firewall to allow access to the "
"URLs required by non-{suse} repositories.  This allows the synchronization "
"process to reach the URLs and complete successfully."
msgstr ""
"最简单的方法是将防火墙配置为允许访问非 {suse} 储存库所需的 URL。这样，同步进"
"程就能访问这些 URL 并成功完成。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:7
msgid ""
"If allowing external traffic is not possible, configure your firewall to "
"``REJECT`` requests from {productname} instead of ``DROP``.  This rejects "
"requests to third-party URLs, so that the synchronization fails early rather "
"than times out, and the products are not shown in the list."
msgstr ""
"如果不能允许外部流量，请将防火墙配置为``拒绝``来自 {productname} 的请求，而不"
"是``丢弃``。这会拒绝对第三方 URL 的请求，因此同步会提前失败而不是超时，并且产"
"品不会显示在列表中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-firewalls.adoc:8
msgid ""
"If you do not have configuration access to the firewall, you can consider "
"setting up a separate firewall on the {productname} Server instead."
msgstr ""
"如果您无权配置防火墙，可以考虑在 {productname} Server 上单独设置一个防火墙。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting high sync times between {productname} Server and Proxy over WAN connections"
msgstr "对通过 WAN 连接在 {productname} Server 与 Proxy 之间同步时间过长的问题进行查错"

#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Depending on what changes are executed in the WebUI or via an API call to "
"distribution or system settings, [literal]``cobbler sync`` command may be "
"required to transfer files from {productname} Server to {productname} Proxy "
"systems.  To accomplish this, cobbler uses a list of proxies specified in "
"[literal]``/etc/cobbler/settings``."
msgstr ""
"根据在 WebUI 中或通过 API 调用对发行套件或系统设置执行的更改，可能需要使用 "
"[literal]``cobbler sync`` 命令将 {productname} Server 中的文件传输到 "
"{productname} Proxy 系统。为此，cobbler 将使用 [literal]``/etc/cobbler/"
"settings`` 中指定的代理列表。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:3
msgid ""
"Due to its design, [literal]``cobbler sync`` is not able to sync only the "
"changed or recently added files."
msgstr "[literal]``cobbler sync`` 在设计上无法仅同步已更改的或最近添加的文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:4
msgid ""
"Instead, executing [literal]``cobbler sync`` triggers a full sync of the "
"[literal]``/srv/tftpboot`` directory to all specified proxies configured in "
"[literal]``/etc/cobbler/settings``.  It is also influenced by the latency of "
"the WAN connection between the involved systems."
msgstr ""
"实际情况是，执行 [literal]``cobbler sync`` 会触发将 [literal]``/srv/"
"tftpboot`` 目录完全同步到 [literal]``/etc/cobbler/settings`` 中配置的所有已指"
"定代理的操作。此命令还会受到相关系统之间 WAN 连接延迟的影响。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The process of syncing may take a considerable amount of time to finish "
"according to the logs in [literal]``/var/log/cobbler/``."
msgstr ""
"根据 [literal]``/var/log/cobbler/`` 中的日志，同步过程可能需要很长时间才能完"
"成。"

