"[literal]``SUMAHOSTNAME``、[literal]``SUMAIP`` 和 [literal]``SUMAPROXY1`` 变"
"量，使其能够正常运行。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:15
