#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:21
msgid "Procedure: Analyze new sync speed"
msgstr "过程：分析新的同步速度"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Take a dump of the TCP traffic between {productname} and the involved "
"systems."
msgstr "为 {productname} 与相关系统之间的 TCP 流量创建转储。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:23
msgid "On SUSE Manager Server:"
msgstr "在 SUSE Manager Server 上："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "tcpdump -i ethX -s 200 host <ip-address-of-susemanagerproxy> and not ssh\n"
msgstr "tcpdump -i ethX -s 200 host <SUSE Manager Proxy 的 IP 地址> and not ssh\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:25
msgid "On SUSE Manager Proxy:"
msgstr "在 SUSE Manager Proxy 上："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "tcpdump -i ethX -s 200 host <ip-address-of-susemanager> and not ssh\n"
msgstr "tcpdump -i ethX -s 200 host <SUSE Manager 的 IP 地址> and not ssh\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:27
msgid ""
"This will only capture a package size of 200 which is sufficient to run an "
"analysis."
msgstr "这样就只会捕获大小为 200 的软件包，但足以运行分析。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Adjust ethX to the respective network interface {productname} uses to "
"communicate with the proxy."
msgstr "将 ethX 调整为由 {productname} 用来与代理通讯的相应网络接口。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:29
msgid ""
"At last, ssh communication will not be captured to reduce the number of "
"packages even further."
msgstr "最后，不会捕获 ssh 通讯，从而进一步减少了软件包的数量。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:30
msgid "Start a cobbler sync."
msgstr "开始 cobbler 同步。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:31
msgid ""
"To force a sync, delete the cobbler json cache file first and then issue "
"cobbler sync:"
msgstr "要强制同步，请先删除 cobbler json 缓存文件，然后发出 cobbler sync："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rm /var/lib/cobbler/pxe_cache.json\n"
"cobbler sync\n"
msgstr ""
"rm /var/lib/cobbler/pxe_cache.json\n"
"cobbler sync\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:33
msgid "When cobbler is finished, stop the TCPdumps."
msgstr "cobbler 完成后，停止 TCPdumps。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:34
msgid ""
"Open the TCPdumps using Wireshark, go to [guimenu]``Statistics > "
"Conversations`` and wait for the dump to be analyzed."
msgstr ""
"使用 Wireshark 打开 TCPdumps，转到 [guimenu]``Statistics（统计信息）> "
"Conversations（对话）``，并等待分析转储。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:35
msgid ""
"Switch to the TCP tab.  The number shown on this tab gives the total number "
"of conversations captured between SUSE Manager and SUSE Manager Proxy."
msgstr ""
"切换到“TCP”选项卡。此选项卡上显示的数字是在 SUSE Manager 与 SUSE Manager "
"Proxy 之间捕获的对话总数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:36
msgid "Look for the column [guimenu]``Duration``."
msgstr "找到列 [guimenu]``Duration（持续时间）``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:37
msgid ""
"Start by sorting in ascending order to find out the minimal amount of time "
"it took to transfer a file."
msgstr "首先按升序排序，找出传输文件所花费的最短时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:38
msgid ""
"Continue by sorting in descending order to find out the maximum values for "
"the big files, for example kernel and initrd transfers."
msgstr "继续按降序排序，找出大文件传输时间的最大值，例如内核和 initrd 传输。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:39
msgid "Ignore ports 4505 and 4506 as these are used for Salt communication."
msgstr "忽略端口 4505 和 4506，因为它们用于 Salt 通讯。"

#. === Conclusion 
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:40
msgid ""
"Analysis of the TCPdumps showed the transfer of small files with a size of "
"approx. 1800 bytes from {productname} Server to Proxy took around 0.3 "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"TCPdumps 分析结果表明，将大小约为 1800 字节的小文件从 {productname} Server 传"
"输到 Proxy 大约花费了 0.3 秒。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:41
msgid ""
"While there were not many big files, the high number of smaller files "
"resulted high number of established connections as new TCP connection is "
"created for every single transferred file."
msgstr ""
"此处的大文件不多，而大量的小文件导致建立了大量连接，因为每传输一个文件就要创"
"建新的 TCP 连接。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:42
msgid ""
"Therefore, knowing the minimal amount of transfer time and a number of "
"connections needed (approx. 5000 in the example), gives an approximate "
"estimated time for the overall transfer time: 5000 * 0.3 / 60 = 25 minutes."
msgstr ""
"因此，在知道最短传输时间和所需连接数（在本示例中大约为 5000）的情况下，可以大"
"致估算出总传输时间：5000 * 0.3 / 60 = 25 分钟。"

#. type: Title =
