#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. Showing my working. --LKB 2020-06-22
#. Cause: Renaming the hostname
#. Consequence: Changes not picked up by db, clients and proxies
#. Fix: Use the [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script to update the settings in the PostgreSQL database and the internal structures of {productname}.
#. Result: Renaming is successfully propagated
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you change the hostname of the {productname} Server locally, your "
"{productname} installation ceases to work properly.  This is because the "
"changes have not been made in the database, which prevents the changes from "
"propagating out your clients and any proxies."
msgstr ""
"如果您在本地更改了 {productname} Server 的主机名，{productname} 安装将无法正"
"常进行。这是因为尚未在数据库中做出相应更改，因而这些更改无法从您的客户端和任"
"何代理传播出来。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:3
msgid ""
"If you need to change the hostname of the {productname} Server, you can do "
"so using the [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script.  This script "
"updates the settings in the PostgreSQL database and the internal structures "
"of {productname}."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要更改 {productname} Server 的主机名，可以使用 [command]``spacewalk-"
"hostname-rename`` 脚本来更改。此脚本会更新 PostgreSQL 数据库以及 "
"{productname} 的内部结构中的设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:4
msgid ""
"The [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script is part of the "
"[package]``spacewalk-utils`` package."
msgstr ""
"[command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` 脚本是 [package]``spacewalk-utils`` 软"
"件包的一部分。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The only mandatory parameter for the script is the newly configured IP "
"address of the {productname} Server."
msgstr "该脚本的唯一必需参数是为 {productname} Server 新配置的 IP 地址。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Renaming {productname} Server"
msgstr "过程：重命名 {productname} Server"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:7
msgid ""
"Change the network settings of the server on the system level locally and "
"remotely at the DNS server."
msgstr "在 DNS 服务器上，本地和远程更改系统级别的服务器的网络设置。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:8
msgid ""
"You also need to provide configuration settings for reverse name "
"resolution.  Changing network settings is done in the same way as with "
"renaming any other system."
msgstr ""
"您还需要提供用于反向名称解析的配置设置。更改网络设置的方式与重命名任何其他系"
"统的方式相同。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Reboot the {productname} Server to use the new network configuration and to "
"ensure the hostname has changed."
msgstr "重引导 {productname} Server 以使用新网络配置并确保主机名更改。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Run the script [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script with the public "
"IP address of the server."
msgstr ""
"结合服务器的公共 IP 地址运行脚本 [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename``。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:11
msgid ""
"If the server is not using the new hostname, the script fails.  Be aware "
"that this script refreshes the pillar data for all Salt minion: the time it "
"takes to run depends on the number of registered Salt systems."
msgstr ""
"如果服务器未使用新主机名，则该脚本会失败。请注意，此脚本会刷新所有 Salt 受控"
"端的 pillar 数据：运行时间取决于已注册的 Salt 系统数。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Re-configure your clients to make your environment aware of the new hostname "
"and IP address."
msgstr "重新配置您的客户端，使您的环境知道新的主机名和 IP 地址。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:13
msgid ""
"In the Salt minion configuration file [path]``/etc/salt/minion``, you must "
"specify the name of the new Salt master ({productname} Server):"
msgstr ""
"在 Salt 受控端配置文件 [path]``/etc/salt/minion`` 中，必须指定新 Salt 主控端"
"的名称 ({productname} Server)："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "master: <new_hostname>\n"
