"When packages on a client are locked, {productname} Server may not be able "
"to correctly determine the set of applicable patches.  When this occurs, "
"package updates are available in the {webui}, but do not appear on the "
"client, and attempts to update the client fail.  Check package locks and "
"exclude lists to determine if packages are locked or excluded on the client."
