#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Registering Cloned Clients"
msgstr "对注册克隆的客户端时出现的问题进行查错"

#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you are using {productname} to manage virtual machines, you might find it "
"useful to create clones of your VMs.  A clone is a VM that uses a primary "
"disk that is an exact copy of an existing disk."
msgstr ""
"如果您使用 {productname} 来管理虚拟机，您可能发现创建 VM 的克隆版本会很有用。"
"克隆版本是使用主磁盘（与现有磁盘完全相同的副本）的 VM。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:3
msgid ""
"While cloning VMs can save you a lot of time, the duplicated identifying "
"information on the disk can sometimes cause problems."
msgstr "虽然克隆 VM 可以节省大量时间，但磁盘上复制的标识信息有时会导致问题。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:4
msgid ""
"If you have a client that is already registered, you create a clone of that "
"client, and then try and register the clone, you probably want {productname} "
"to register them as two separate clients.  However, if the machine ID in "
"both the original client and the clone is the same, {productname} registers "
"both clients as one system, and the existing client data is overwritten with "
"that of the clone."
msgstr ""
"如果您有一个已注册的客户端，并创建了该客户端的克隆版本，在尝试注册该克隆版本"
"时，您可能希望 {productname} 将原始客户端和克隆版本注册为两个不同的客户端。但"
"是，如果原始客户端和克隆版本中的计算机 ID 相同，则 {productname} 会将这两个客"
"户端注册为一个系统，并且现有客户端数据将由克隆版本的数据重写。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:5
msgid ""
"This can be resolved by changing the machine ID of the clone, so that "
"{productname} recognizes them as two different clients."
msgstr ""
"可以通过更改克隆版本的计算机 ID 来解决此问题，以便 {productname} 将它们识别为"
"两个不同的客户端。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Each step of this procedure is performed on the cloned client.  This "
"procedure does not manipulate the original client, which remains registered "
"to {productname}."
msgstr ""
"此过程的每个步骤都在克隆的客户端上执行。此过程不会对原始客户端进行操作，原始"
"客户端仍保持注册到 {productname}。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Resolving Duplicate Machine IDs in Cloned Salt Clients"
msgstr "过程：解决克隆的 Salt 客户端中的重复计算机 ID"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:8
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:23
msgid "On the cloned machine, change the hostname and IP addresses."
msgstr "在克隆的计算机上，更改主机名和 IP 地址。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:9
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:24
msgid ""
"Make sure [path]``/etc/hosts`` contains the changes you made and the correct "
"host entries."
msgstr "确保 [path]``/etc/hosts`` 包含您所做的更改和正确的主机项。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:10
msgid ""
"For distributions that support systemd: If your machines have the same "
"machine ID, as root, delete the files on each duplicated client and re-"
"create it:"
msgstr ""
"对于支持 systemd 的发行套件：如果您的计算机具有相同的计算机 ID，请以 root 身"
"份删除复制的每个客户端上的文件，然后重新创建这些文件："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rm /etc/machine-id\n"
"rm /var/lib/dbus/machine-id\n"
"rm /var/lib/zypp/AnonymousUniqueId\n"
"dbus-uuidgen --ensure\n"
"systemd-machine-id-setup\n"
msgstr ""
"rm /etc/machine-id\n"
"rm /var/lib/dbus/machine-id\n"
"rm /var/lib/zypp/AnonymousUniqueId\n"
"dbus-uuidgen --ensure\n"
"systemd-machine-id-setup\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:12
msgid ""
"For distributions that do not support systemd: As root, generate a machine "
"ID from dbus:"
msgstr "对于不支持 systemd 的发行套件：以 root 身份从 dbus 生成计算机 ID："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rm /var/lib/dbus/machine-id\n"
"rm /var/lib/zypp/AnonymousUniqueId\n"
"dbus-uuidgen --ensure\n"
msgstr ""
"rm /var/lib/dbus/machine-id\n"
"rm /var/lib/zypp/AnonymousUniqueId\n"
"dbus-uuidgen --ensure\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:14
msgid ""
"If your clients still have the same Salt client ID, delete the "
"[path]``minion_id`` file on each client (FQDN is used when it is regenerated "
"on client restart).  For Salt Minion clients:"
msgstr ""
"如果您的客户端仍然具有相同的 Salt 客户端 ID，请删除每个客户端上的 "
"[path]``minion_id`` 文件（这样就会使用在客户端重启动时重新生成的 FQDN）。对"
"于 Salt 受控端客户端："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rm /etc/salt/minion_id\n"
"rm -rf /etc/salt/pki\n"
msgstr ""
"rm /etc/salt/minion_id\n"
"rm -rf /etc/salt/pki\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:16
msgid "For Salt Bundle clients:"
msgstr "对于 Salt 捆绑包客户端："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rm /etc/venv-salt-minion/minion_id\n"
"rm -rf /etc/venv-salt-minion/pki\n"
msgstr ""
"rm /etc/venv-salt-minion/minion_id\n"
"rm -rf /etc/venv-salt-minion/pki\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Delete accepted keys from the onboarding page and the system profile from "
"{productname}, and restart the client with:"
msgstr ""
"从初始配置页面中删除接受的密钥并从 {productname} 中删除系统配置文件，然后使用"
"以下命令重启动客户端："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "service salt-minion restart\n"
msgstr "service salt-minion restart\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:20
msgid "Re-register the clients."
msgstr "重新注册客户端。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:21
msgid ""
"Each client now has a different [path]``/etc/machine-id`` and should be "
"correctly displayed on the [guimenu]``System Overview`` page."
msgstr ""
"每个客户端现在都有一个不同的 [path]``/etc/machine-id``，并且应会正确显示在"
"[guimenu]``系统概览``页面上。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Resolving Duplicate Machine IDs in Cloned Traditional Clients"
msgstr "过程：解决克隆的传统客户端中的重复计算机 ID"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:25
msgid ""
"Stop the [systemitem]``rhnsd`` daemon, on {rhnminrelease6} and {sle} 11 with:"
msgstr ""
"在 {rhnminrelease6} 和 {sle} 11 上使用以下命令停止 [systemitem]``rhnsd`` 守护"
"程序："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/init.d/rhnsd stop\n"
msgstr "/etc/init.d/rhnsd stop\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:27
msgid "or, on newer systemd-based systems, with:"
msgstr "或者，在基于 systemd 的较新系统上使用以下命令："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "service rhnsd stop\n"
msgstr "service rhnsd stop\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:29
msgid "Stop [systemitem]``osad`` with:"
msgstr "使用以下命令停止 [systemitem]``osad``："

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-registerclones.adoc:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "/etc/init.d/osad stop\n"
msgstr "/etc/init.d/osad stop\n"

